Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,美国派拉蒙影片公司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,美国天空之舞制片公司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,无论生死皆隐于世\N{\rE}We live and die in the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只为我们珍爱之人\N{\rE}for those we hold close
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,也为不曾谋面之人\N{\rE}and for those we never meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕看到的那个结局 就快来了\N{\rE}The end you always feared is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,反上帝\N{\rE}The Anti-God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这个"智体"有多重的身份\N{\rE}This "entity" has multiple personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是它会自主思考了吗\N{\rE}You're telling me this thing has a mind of its own?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一只具有意识 可以自主学习 吞噬真相的数字寄生虫\N{\rE}A self-aware, self-learning, truth-eating digital parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,正滋生于整个网络之中\N{\rE}infesting all of cyberspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一个无处不在的敌人 同时又无处可寻 虚无缥缈的敌人\N{\rE}An enemy that is everywhere and nowhere and has no center.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,耐心地倾听 读取 观察我们\N{\rE}Patiently listening, reading, watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,收集我们最私密的个人信息 年复一年\N{\rE}Harvesting our deepest personal secrets for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,它可以欺骗 勒索 贿赂任何人 甚至成为它想成为的人\N{\rE}Able to beguile, blackmail, bribe or be anyone it wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 那不是我 和你说话的是智体\N{\rE}Ethan, that is not me! You're talking to the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,掌握智体就等于掌握了真相\N{\rE}Whoever controls the Entity controls the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,安全中心的数据库遭到入侵和破坏\N{\rE}...most secure data centers are breached and corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,智体非常清楚如何削弱我们的优势\N{\rE}The Entity will know precisely how to undermine our every strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,将我们的盟友变成敌人\N{\rE}Turn our allies into enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,并准确利用我们的弱势\N{\rE}And exploit our every weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,将我们的敌人变成侵略者\N{\rE}...and our enemies into aggressors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一股无法阻止的毁灭力量 将会毁灭一切\N{\rE}An unstoppable force of destructive power that would just lay waste to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,世界正在改变 真相逐渐模糊\N{\rE}The world is changing. Truth is vanishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,战争即将爆发\N{\rE}War is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,碟中谍小组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好 伊森\N{\rE}Good evening, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是总统埃丽卡\N{\rE}This is your president.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你不愿意回复任何人\N{\rE}Since you won't reply to anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,美利坚合众国 总统印章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就干脆直接联系你吧\N{\rE}I thought I'd reach out directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 我想感谢你\N{\rE}First, I want to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你一直以来的奉献\N{\rE}for a lifetime of devoted and unrelenting service.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你和你的伙伴们的坚持不懈 不断努力\N{\rE}Were it not for the tireless dedication of you and your team,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,否则这个世界恐怕早就不得安宁了\N{\rE}the Earth would be a very different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至可能早就已经不存在了\N{\rE}It might not even be here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你经历的每一个生死瞬间\N{\rE}Every risk you've taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,执行任务时你失去的每一位战友\N{\rE}every comrade you've lost in the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,以及你的每一次牺牲\N{\rE}every personal sacrifice you made...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,都再次给这个世界 带来了光明\N{\rE}has brought this world another sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如今35年过去了 当年的局势让你重新回到我们身边\N{\rE}It's been 35 years since circumstances brought you to us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,并给了你选择的机会\N{\rE}and you were given the choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,当时碟中谍小组救了你\N{\rE}since the IMF saved you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,让你免受监禁之苦\N{\rE}from a life in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,即便你一向都不按命令行事\N{\rE}And though you never followed orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但你也从未让我们失望\N{\rE}you never let us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在每个最危急的时刻\N{\rE}You were always the best of men...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是能力挽狂澜\N{\rE}in the worst of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你再次肩负重任\N{\rE}I need you to be that man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你在奥地利逃避抓捕的这几个月里\N{\rE}In the months since you evaded capture in Austria,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,网络空间的每个角落 都充斥着那个吞噬真相的\N{\rE}every corner of cyberspace has been infested by the truth-eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,寄生型人工智能 也可以称之为"智体"\N{\rE}parasitic A.I. known to us as the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,受它的影响\N{\rE}Under its influence,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,全球的数字信息库都遭到了入侵\N{\rE}digital information has been corrupted worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,各国政府和人民都不知道该相信什么\N{\rE}Nations and people no longer know what to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,敌对 侵略和高压管制 成了新的世界秩序\N{\rE}Antagonism, aggression and martial law are the new world order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种满是猜忌的氛围之下\N{\rE}Exploiting this paranoid atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,智体催生出了一个末日邪教\N{\rE}the Entity has inspired a doomsday cult
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,它的信徒致力于通过用灭绝人类的方式\N{\rE}with acolytes devoted to ridding the world of corruption
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,消除世界的腐败\N{\rE}through human extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他对诺亚说 看吧\N{\rE}And He said unto Noah, "Behold..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我要将滔天洪水引向世间\N{\rE}"I will bring a flood upon the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,让所有肉身灰飞烟灭\N{\rE}to destroy all flesh."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,原子之子必将诞生于灰烬之中\N{\rE}The children of the atom shall rise from the ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,智体将帮助他们重建世界\N{\rE}And the Entity will help them rebuild.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这些狂热分子正向执法部门 政府 以及我们军队的\N{\rE}These fanatics are secretly infiltrating every level of law enforcement,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,各个层级秘密渗透\N{\rE}government and our military,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,目的是帮助他们的数字主人实现终极目标\N{\rE}devoted to serving their digital master's ultimate goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们唯一能控制智体的途径\N{\rE}Our only hope of controlling the Entity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就是找到它的初始源代码\N{\rE}relies on finding its original source code.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,至于源代码的下落 只有这个人知晓\N{\rE}If anyone knows the whereabouts of this code, it's this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他的身份 阅历 行踪 统统被抹除了\N{\rE}His identity, his past, his very existence have been erased,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,说明这个人与智体合谋 或者合作过\N{\rE}suggesting he is or was in league with the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,奥地利当局已经拘留了他的同伙\N{\rE}Austrian authorities have his accomplice in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但她什么信息都没交代\N{\rE}But she has refused to tell us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们只好来找你\N{\rE}Which brings us back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手上有一把钥匙 据说这把钥匙\N{\rE}You are in possession of a key believed to be a vital component
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,正是我们获取智体源代码的关键\N{\rE}in our struggle to acquire the Entity's source code.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 你却拒绝自首\N{\rE}Yet you refuse to come in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森·亨特 失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你担心有政府将这个恶意的人工智能用作武器\N{\rE}fearing any government will weaponize this malicious A.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,拿来对付全世界\N{\rE}against the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 你铁了心要除掉智体\N{\rE}Instead you've resolved to kill the Entity,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这种鲁莽的行为 会导致网络空间被完全摧毁\N{\rE}a reckless act that would trigger the total annihilation of cyberspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,使得全球经济毁于一旦\N{\rE}This would eradicate the global economy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,让世界陷入无穷无尽的战乱和饥荒之中\N{\rE}plunging the world into war and famine without end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,亨特探员 伊森\N{\rE}Agent Hunt. Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请你配合我们\N{\rE}Please surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,否则你的双手将沾满世界的鲜血\N{\rE}Or the blood of the world will be on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这条信息五秒钟之后会自动销毁\N{\rE}This message will self-destruct in five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,回来吧 伊森\N{\rE}Come home, Ethan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,把那把钥匙交给我们\N{\rE}and bring us that key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻毁灭 立刻毁灭\N{\rE}End it now! End it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻毁灭 立刻毁灭\N{\rE}End it now! End it now! End it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻毁灭 立刻毁灭\N{\rE}End it now! End it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻毁灭 立刻毁灭\N{\rE}End it now! End it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻毁灭 立刻毁灭\N{\rE}End it now! End it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻毁灭 立刻毁灭\N{\rE}End it now! End it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻毁灭 立刻毁灭\N{\rE}End it now! End it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,警告 此地已充公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森\N{\rE}Hey, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,卢瑟\N{\rE}Hey, Luther.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,条件简陋多担待 豪华酒店都订满了\N{\rE}Sorry about the decor. The Ritz was booked solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,起码有窗帘 几个抱枕 还有\N{\rE}Well, some drapes, a few throw pillows, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 还有小冰箱\N{\rE}Yeah, a minibar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,桌上足球台\N{\rE}Foosball table.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟\N{\rE}Hey, bro. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看见你还活着 我就已经心满意足了\N{\rE}It's always good to see you on the right side of the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心你太辛苦了\N{\rE}I'm worried you're working too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不用替老卢瑟操心\N{\rE}Don't worry about ol' Luther.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rE}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你查到什么了\N{\rE}So, what did you manage to find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不少\N{\rE}A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,比我预料的要多\N{\rE}More than I bargained for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那有什么计划\N{\rE}So, what's the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,首先\N{\rE}First,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得找到盖布瑞尔\N{\rE}we have to find Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么才能找到他呢\N{\rE}How do we find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉茨-卡尔劳监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,奥地利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你会背叛我们\N{\rE}You will betray us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他之前饶了你一命\N{\rE}because he spared your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]住手 住手\N{\rE}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 住手\N{\rE}Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\rE}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要饶我一命\N{\rE}did you spare my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 慢着\N{\rE}Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你如果敢汇报 那世界就完蛋了 就这么简单\N{\rE}You call that in, it's the end of the world- simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫德加 对吧\N{\rE}Degas, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,时间宝贵\N{\rE}Clock is running.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你抓了我们 就没有人能阻止智体了\N{\rE}You take us in, there won't be anyone on Earth who can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点你很清楚\N{\rE}There's a part of you that knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我看得出来\N{\rE}I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真是够了 你就相信他吧 等等 慢着\N{\rE}For God's sake, just trust him! Wait, wait, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱来 别乱来\N{\rE}It's okay, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,德加 别紧张 这事没有国家之分\N{\rE}Degas, it's okay. There's no nations on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不存在要与谁敌对 也没有教条\N{\rE}There's no rival ideologies, no dogma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,关键是谁该冷静 谁该紧张\N{\rE}It's who keeps their head and who panics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,智体想让你恐慌 让我们所有人恐慌\N{\rE}The Entity wants you scared, it wants us all scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它想让我们搞分裂\N{\rE}It wants us divided.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,它想让你把我们抓起来\N{\rE}It wants you to turn us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别上当\N{\rE}Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会有事的\N{\rE}He's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 德加\N{\rE}Please, Degas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮忙\N{\rE}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是朋友\N{\rE}We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]盖布瑞尔\N{\rE}[in French]Gabriel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]他在哪里\N{\rE}[in French]Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,美国大使馆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有增援 你怎么能进去呢\N{\rE}You shouldn't be in there without backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,班吉 行啦 我们能搞定\N{\rE}Benji, please. We got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么破主意 放宽心\N{\rE}This is a terrible idea. Just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 这里到处都是特工\N{\rE}Ethan, this place is crawling with clandestine services.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你得快点离开\N{\rE}You should get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看到他们了 没事的 不要慌 班吉\N{\rE}I see them. It's okay. Stay calm, Benji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔怎么可能冒险去这次宴会呢\N{\rE}I don't think Gabriel would risk coming to that party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快撤吧\N{\rE}Abort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不 咱们都先冷静一下 他在这儿\N{\rE}No, let's just hold our nerve. He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定在这儿\N{\rE}He's got to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 求你了 赶紧撤 总会有办法的\N{\rE}Ethan, for God's sake, abort! We'll figure this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,目前问题不大\N{\rE}Not a problem yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,站着别动\N{\rE}Stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱动 亨特\N{\rE}Don't move, Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们确定真的是我吗\N{\rE}Are you sure it's really me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,各小组注意 发现亨特了 重复 发现亨特了\N{\rE}All units, we have Hunt. I repeat, we have Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们听不到\N{\rE}They can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rE}Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么时候拿走的\N{\rE}I didn't even see you get that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,让神偷和小偷拉开差距的关键是什么\N{\rE}What separates a good pickpocket from a great one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,时机\N{\rE}Timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,两位先生\N{\rE}Gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢往后退\N{\rE}Nice and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我对事不对人\N{\rE}Nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 我喜欢你留长发\N{\rE}You know, I like the longer hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你能来我真的非常感动 但是你不应该来这儿\N{\rE}I really appreciate your coming, but you shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我没得选\N{\rE}I didn't have much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要让我背叛他吗\N{\rE}Will you expect me to betray him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是要让你阻止他 以免他越陷越深\N{\rE}I expect you to save him from himself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,并从他手中拯救世界\N{\rE}and the world from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,基特里奇\N{\rE}Kittridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你这次算是惹上大麻烦了 格蕾丝\N{\rE}You just bought yourself a world of trouble, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界都惹上麻烦了 伊森\N{\rE}The whole world's in trouble, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信只有你才能够拯救世界\N{\rE}You're the only one I trust to save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你有什么计划\N{\rE}So, what's the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rE}Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rE}Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔有任务安排给你 亨特\N{\rE}Gabriel's got a job for you, Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 醒醒\N{\rE}Ethan, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快说 该怎么办\N{\rE}Okay, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别跟我说你没计划\N{\rE}Tell me you have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手表被摘走了\N{\rE}They took my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手表 对 还有我的袖扣\N{\rE}Your watch? Yeah, and my cuff links.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有撬锁工具 知道了\N{\rE}Had lock picks in them. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,另想办法出去 好吧 听着\N{\rE}We'll find a way out, okay? Now, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来不及了\N{\rE}Ah, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始了\N{\rE}It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 格蕾丝 看着我\N{\rE}Okay, Grace, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你能挺过去的\N{\rE}You're gonna get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,挺过去什么\N{\rE}Get through what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你就一直跟自己说\N{\rE}Just keep telling yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,疼痛不算什么\N{\rE}it's only pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 不许碰他\N{\rE}Stop! Don't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样没用的\N{\rE}You can't hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,伤不了他\N{\rE}Not that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,像不像梦回上海\N{\rE}Take you back to Shanghai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫什么来着\N{\rE}What was her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉娅\N{\rE}Julia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,以前叫亨特太太\N{\rE}The former Mrs. Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森没有提起过她吗\N{\rE}Did Ethan fail to mention her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一个叫戴维恩的人劫持了她\N{\rE}A fellow named Davian took her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,然后用她去索要赎金\N{\rE}and ransomed her for something
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要求用一样只有伊森能搞到的东西 来赎她\N{\rE}only Ethan could get.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,戴维恩把它叫作"兔脚"\N{\rE}Davian called it the Rabbit's Foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但它还有个名字\N{\rE}But it had another name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,反上帝\N{\rE}The Anti-God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没告诉过你罐子里装的是什么吧\N{\rE}They never told you what was in that canister, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但你总是很好奇\N{\rE}But you always wondered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,偷走"兔脚" 不过是人生中的一次任务\N{\rE}Stealing the Rabbit's Foot was just one event in a lifelong pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一次又一次地重复\N{\rE}repeating itself over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他每拯救一条生命 都要赌上\N{\rE}For every life he's tried to save, he's gambled millions more,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,几百万条性命\N{\rE}doubling down and down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:16:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一次又一次地加码 现如今地球上每一条生命的命运\N{\rE}And now the fate of every living soul on Earth is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都成为了他的责任\N{\rE}his responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定累坏了吧\N{\rE}You must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙在哪\N{\rE}Where's the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,放了她\N{\rE}Let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们再谈 别耽误时间了\N{\rE}Then we'll discuss it. We don't have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,某个你珍爱的人今晚即将死去\N{\rE}Someone you hold close will die tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还谈什么为了不曾谋面之人\N{\rE}for the sake of those you will never meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你乖乖照我说的做\N{\rE}unless you do exactly as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在火车上他说过钥匙会归他 记得吗\N{\rE}He also said the key would be his on the train, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有一项任务\N{\rE}You had one job:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,上火车 拿钥匙 下火车\N{\rE}Get on the train, get the key, get off the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老板要是知道你任务失败 又会作何感想呢\N{\rE}How did your master take the news when it found out you blew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你失败了\N{\rE}You failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在智体已经抛弃了你\N{\rE}and now the Entity has forsaken you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的团队已经暴露了 伊森\N{\rE}Your team's been compromised, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道卢瑟在做什么 也清楚你的计划\N{\rE}I know what Luther's doing. I know what you're planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我作对 就要付出惨痛的代价\N{\rE}Resist me and I'll make you pay dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖合作的话\N{\rE}If you cooperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你\N{\rE}I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你的条件是什么\N{\rE}In exchange for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你去找一艘俄罗斯潜艇 它在首航中突然失踪了\N{\rE}You're searching for a Russian submarine vanished on its maiden voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,K559塞瓦斯托波尔号\N{\rE}The K559 Sevastopol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是目前最先进的潜艇 所有声纳技术都探测不到它\N{\rE}A state-of-the-art submarine completely undetectable to any known sonar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它能隐形的秘密就在于那个东西\N{\rE}And the secret to its invisibility was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,马蹄铁\N{\rE}The Podkova.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一个反声学算法驱动器\N{\rE}A counter-acoustic algorithmic drive
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,装在塞瓦斯托波尔号的声纳球里\N{\rE}located in the Sevastopol's sonar sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在2012年冬天\N{\rE}Now, in the winter of 2012
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,俄国人发现了一种来历不明的电脑病毒\N{\rE}the Russians discovered a computer virus of unknown origin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在黑海舰队中传播\N{\rE}spreading through their Black Sea fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是数字秘密特工所为\N{\rE}A digital covert operative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怀疑这个神秘病毒\N{\rE}We suspect this mystery virus was only intended
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,只是为了破坏马蹄铁 让潜艇可以被雷达探测到\N{\rE}to sabotage the Podkova, rendering the submarine detectable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 它欺骗了潜艇官 把船弄沉了\N{\rE}Instead... It tricked the crew into sinking themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长 我方鱼雷没有响应\N{\rE}Captain! Our own torpedo is not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,正在朝我们袭来\N{\rE}It's coming right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被锁定了 打击距离400米\N{\rE}Our torpedo's homing! Range 400 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,拉响碰撞警报\N{\rE}Sound the collision alar--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们是对的 除掉智体所需要的东西就是\N{\rE}If we're right, the one thing we need to kill the Entity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,它的初始源代码\N{\rE}its original source code,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就在塞瓦斯托波尔号的声纳球里\N{\rE}is buried in the Sevastopol's sonar sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它在海底深处的某个地方 尘封在时间里\N{\rE}Somewhere deep at the bottom of the ocean, frozen in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在智体都无法到达的地方\N{\rE}where even the Entity can't reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,马蹄铁的外部结构经过特别设计\N{\rE}Now, the Podkova's housing was designed to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦遭到破坏就会启动自毁程序\N{\rE}self-destruct if tampered with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想要完好地将它打开\N{\rE}The only way to safely open it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就需要特制的十字形钥匙\N{\rE}is with a specially designed cruciform key.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙分为两片 在塞瓦斯托波尔号的艇长和副艇长手上\N{\rE}The two halves of which were held by the Sevastopol's captain and XO.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就在2012年的春天\N{\rE}They were pulled from the drifting pack ice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因纽特渔民从浮冰中\N{\rE}in the spring of 2012
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,取出了这两片钥匙\N{\rE}by Inuit fishermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这样优秀的人才\N{\rE}A man of your skills
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想必以你现在的能力 应该能精确定位潜艇的位置吧\N{\rE}now has all he needs to pinpoint that sub down to the square yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我把源代码取回来就会交给你吗\N{\rE}You think I'm gonna get the source code and bring it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不用以为 我确定\N{\rE}I don't think. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算放你走\N{\rE}I'm gonna let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你会找到智体的源代码 再把它交给我\N{\rE}Then you're gonna find the Entity's source code and bring it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用来交换格蕾丝\N{\rE}in exchange for Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我将控制智体\N{\rE}Then I'll take control of the Entity,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,而你会成为放出释放这个妖魔的罪魁祸首\N{\rE}the proverbial genie you let out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,兔脚\N{\rE}The Rabbit's Foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,反上帝\N{\rE}The Anti-God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你从上海带走的不是生化武器\N{\rE}It wasn't a biological or a chemical weapon you took from Shanghai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你交换茱莉娅的瓶子里装着恶意代码\N{\rE}The vial you traded for Julia contained malicious code.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那个初始的数字化浆液\N{\rE}The primordial digital ooze
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,演化成了一种武器\N{\rE}from which a weapon evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,之前东方国家还不擅使用\N{\rE}A weapon the East couldn't make work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而西方国家也永远造不出来\N{\rE}A weapon the West might never have made on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道自己偷的是什么\N{\rE}You didn't know what you were stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都不知道\N{\rE}None of us did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我为什么要去偷\N{\rE}I knew why I was stealing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们绑架了我的妻子\N{\rE}They kidnapped my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,去偷兔脚是我唯一能救回妻子的方法\N{\rE}Stealing the Rabbit's Foot was the only way I could get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,潜艇是智体弄沉的 也是我弄沉的\N{\rE}I sank that submarine as much as the Entity did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是你 伊森\N{\rE}Without you, Ethan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,智体就不会存在\N{\rE}there'd be no Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在接下来的几天里没能找到潜艇\N{\rE}And if you don't find that sub in the next few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么世界末日就要来临了\N{\rE}It's the end of the world as we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候他就铸成大错了\N{\rE}And it will all be his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他很清楚\N{\rE}He knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\rE}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的不对吗\N{\rE}Tell me I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,假牙里\N{\rE}False tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是氰化物胶囊\N{\rE}Cyanide capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我咬破它 60秒内就会丧命\N{\rE}I bite down on this, and I'm dead in sixty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你就永远都得不到源代码了\N{\rE}You'll never see that source code.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要碰他\N{\rE}Don't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,吐出来吧\N{\rE}Spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,先把她放了\N{\rE}Release her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会自尽\N{\rE}You won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都能豁出去\N{\rE}I got nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝怎么办\N{\rE}But Grace does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你死了\N{\rE}And with you dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来救她出去呢\N{\rE}who's gonna save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快吐出来 伊森\N{\rE}Spit it out. Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,记住 格蕾丝 疼痛不算什么\N{\rE}Remember, Grace, it's only pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,医护人员 伊森\N{\rE}Medic! Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,去拿除颤仪\N{\rE}Bring the defibrillator!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快\N{\rE}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快 赶快\N{\rE}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 正在充电\N{\rE}Wait, wait! Charging.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,正在充电\N{\rE}Charging.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,准备\N{\rE}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙\N{\rE}Keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对他得留活口\N{\rE}I need him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把她杀了\N{\rE}Kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔要溜了\N{\rE}Gabriel's getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,动手\N{\rE}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森\N{\rE}Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\rE}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔要跑了\N{\rE}Gabriel's getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rE}Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rE}Whoa. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是以为我会让他们\N{\rE}You don't think that I would have let them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 我绝不会让你受伤害\N{\rE}Grace, I would never let anything happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,最起码 不受严重伤害\N{\rE}Nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\rE}I mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rE}Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.97,0:22:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\rE}I mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟他们要杀你\N{\rE}Well, they were gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对\N{\rE}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对\N{\rE}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你表现得很不错\N{\rE}Hey, you did great, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:22:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们真的得走了\N{\rE}We really got to go.
