Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.55,0:24:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,视效制片人\N{\rE}罗宾·萨克森
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拦住他了\N{\rE}I got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.27,0:24:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,之前不是说了吗 伊森要抓活的\N{\rE}We talked about this. Ethan wants him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.32,0:24:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]我要他死\N{\rE}[in French]I want him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.15,0:24:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,迟早要被她害死\N{\rE}She'll be the death of me.
