Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.69,0:24:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,服装设计\N{\rE}吉尔·泰勒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.93,0:24:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森\N{\rE}Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:25:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,剪辑\N{\rE}埃迪·汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.99,0:25:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]这是什么\N{\rE}[Ethan in French]What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.74,0:25:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]他用这个来跟智体对话\N{\rE}[in French]It's how he spoke to it.
