Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.46,0:25:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,根据布鲁斯·盖勒\N{\rE}原创电视剧集改编
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.44,0:26:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,编剧\N{\rE}克里斯托夫·迈考利
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.06,0:26:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,埃里克·延德雷森
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.21,0:26:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会真的打算\N{\rE}You're not seriously gonna...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.51,0:26:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]智体会将你改变\N{\rE}[in French]It will change you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.76,0:26:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,导演\N{\rE}克里斯托夫·迈考利
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.45,0:26:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 我来了\N{\rE}All right, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.95,0:26:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想怎么样\N{\rE}Now what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.04,0:26:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好 亨特先生\N{\rE}Good evening, Mr. Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.51,0:26:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你有很多疑问\N{\rE}You have questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.51,0:26:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,智体能告诉你答案\N{\rE}The Entity has answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.22,0:26:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但你必须放弃抵抗\N{\rE}But you have to let it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.35,0:27:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这个地方\N{\rE}You know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.86,0:27:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持抵抗 只会更痛苦\N{\rE}There is only pain if you resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.03,0:27:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次\N{\rE}Again,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.53,0:27:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这个地方\N{\rE}you know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.54,0:27:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,末日保险库\N{\rE}The Doomsday Vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.41,0:27:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在南非\N{\rE}South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.75,0:27:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你会在那儿见到智体\N{\rE}You will meet the Entity there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.29,0:27:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你会让智体进入\N{\rE}You will let it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.84,0:27:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那里会决定每个生命的命运\N{\rE}And the fate of every living thing will be decided
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.92,0:27:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都只要\N{\rE}in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.30,0:27:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一眨眼的功夫 这就是你的使命\N{\rE}This is your calling, your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.89,0:27:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的命运 我不答应\N{\rE}I don't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.73,0:27:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 你没有秘密可言\N{\rE}In here, you have no secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.78,0:27:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,K559 塞瓦斯托波尔号\N{\rE}The K559 Sevastopol.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.28,0:27:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,马蹄铁\N{\rE}The Podkova.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.57,0:28:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,十字形钥匙\N{\rE}A cruciform key.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.07,0:28:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的得意之作\N{\rE}My magnum opus.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.41,0:28:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等闪存里的算法\N{\rE}The algorithm on that drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.75,0:28:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,与智体的源代码配对之后\N{\rE}when paired with the Entity's source code,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.33,0:28:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就会按你要求的那样激活病毒闪存\N{\rE}will act as the poison pill you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.59,0:28:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算去找塞瓦斯托波尔号取回马蹄铁\N{\rE}You plan to retrieve the Podkova from the Sevastopol
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.26,0:28:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,然后将智体摧毁\N{\rE}and destroy the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.47,0:28:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你因此感到害怕\N{\rE}And that scares you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.26,0:28:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,智体可以看见无限种可能性\N{\rE}The Entity sees infinite possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.68,0:28:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,取回马蹄铁\N{\rE}Retrieve the Podkova
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.60,0:28:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在孤注一掷\N{\rE}and you risk everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.28,0:28:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去末日保险库\N{\rE}You will go to the Doomsday Vault
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.91,0:28:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让智体进入\N{\rE}and let the Entity in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.33,0:28:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都已成定局\N{\rE}It is written.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.91,0:28:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\rE}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.21,0:28:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,末日即将到来 伊森\N{\rE}The end is coming, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.46,0:28:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你心里一直都很清楚\N{\rE}You have always known this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.88,0:28:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,智体可以让未来充满希望\N{\rE}The Entity offers hope for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.30,0:29:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,幸存下来的少数人会变得更强大\N{\rE}The few who survive will be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.13,0:29:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,原子之子必将诞生于灰烬之中\N{\rE}The children of the atom shall rise from the ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.80,0:29:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,智体将帮助他们重建世界\N{\rE}And the Entity will help them rebuild.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.47,0:29:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,前提是你让智体进入\N{\rE}But only if you let it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.43,0:29:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不答应呢\N{\rE}And if I don't... what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.98,0:29:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁这个世界 就等于你摧毁了自己\N{\rE}Destroy the world and you just destroy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.07,0:29:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,选择权在你手上\N{\rE}The choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.36,0:29:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,选择有智体的未来\N{\rE}The Entity's future
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.11,0:29:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还是选择断送未来\N{\rE}or no future at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.07,0:29:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是选择让世界被奴役\N{\rE}Let the world be enslaved
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.41,0:29:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还是选择让世界被毁灭\N{\rE}or let the world be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.49,0:29:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在已经被选中\N{\rE}Now you are the chosen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.54,0:29:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔已经被抛弃\N{\rE}Gabriel is outcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.54,0:29:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经开始着手行动企图控制智体 正如你将看见的\N{\rE}He has taken steps to gain control of the Entity, as you will see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.01,0:29:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我作对 就要付出惨痛的代价\N{\rE}Resist me and I'll make you pay dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.01,0:29:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,某个你珍爱的人今晚即将死去\N{\rE}Someone you hold close will die tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.18,0:29:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,卢瑟\N{\rE}Luther.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.23,0:29:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道人类必须怎么做才能改变自己的命运\N{\rE}You know what humanity must do to change their destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.06,0:29:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们无法阻止注定的结局\N{\rE}You know they cannot stop the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.86,0:30:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会觉得没有选择的余地 最终自我毁灭\N{\rE}They will destroy themselves believing they have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.36,0:30:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的气数将尽\N{\rE}Their time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.37,0:30:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,再过四天\N{\rE}In four days,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.87,0:30:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就要面临最终清算\N{\rE}they will face their final reckoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.52,0:31:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是真的吗 这都是真的吗\N{\rE}Is this real? Is this real?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.23,0:31:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rE}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.32,0:31:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你是真的 你是真的\N{\rE}Are you real? You're real.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.32,0:31:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你是真的\N{\rE}You're real. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.99,0:31:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,它都知道了 它知道什么了\N{\rE}It knows. It knows what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.99,0:31:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,给我支笔 我要写点东西\N{\rE}I need a pen. Something to write on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.29,0:31:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,团队交给你了 你带大家去北边\N{\rE}You'll take the team. You'll take them north.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.79,0:31:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,去北边哪里\N{\rE}North? North where?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.58,0:31:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,塞瓦斯托波尔号 塞瓦斯托波尔号\N{\rE}The Sevastopol. The Sevastopol?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.42,0:31:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须被拘捕 只有这样才能去那儿\N{\rE}I have to get caught. It's the only way I could get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.50,0:31:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,甚高频接收器 还有减压舱\N{\rE}VHF receiver. Decompression chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.09,0:31:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,偷一架飞机 旧飞机 不要应答器 不要定位系统\N{\rE}Steal a plane. An old plane. No transponder, no GPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.30,0:31:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,全用模拟信号\N{\rE}Everything is analog.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.88,0:31:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,DC-3飞机\N{\rE}A DC-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.18,0:31:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要的东西都在上面了\N{\rE}Everything you need is right in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.14,0:31:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,记住每两小时传送一次坐标 广播15分钟\N{\rE}Remember to transmit the coordinates every two hours for 15 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.14,0:31:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想办法接收\N{\rE}and I'll listen when I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.02,0:31:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是队长了 不 我\N{\rE}You're team leader now. No, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.31,0:31:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,班吉 你要照顾好所有人\N{\rE}Benj, take care of your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.02,0:32:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙\N{\rE}Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.19,0:32:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你要远离冰层 什么冰层\N{\rE}You stay off the ice. What ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.11,0:32:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,千万记住 无论怎么样 你都要远离冰层\N{\rE}Just please, whatever you do, no matter what, stay off the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.61,0:32:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好的 好\N{\rE}Okay. Okay. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.86,0:32:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\rE}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.62,0:32:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那你去哪里\N{\rE}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.08,0:32:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,找卢瑟\N{\rE}Luther.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.56,0:32:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,声监系统
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.76,0:33:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉伊森\N{\rE}Tell Ethan...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.76,0:33:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我会等着他的\N{\rE}I'll be waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.17,0:34:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,警告 此地已充公
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.68,0:34:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,卢瑟\N{\rE}Hey, Luther.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.93,0:34:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森\N{\rE}Hey, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.14,0:34:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔的事怎么样了\N{\rE}How'd it go with Gabriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.69,0:34:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,进展得还算顺利 我们\N{\rE}Yeah, it went well. We...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.35,0:34:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\rE}You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.98,0:34:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你身上沾了谁的血\N{\rE}And so, whose blood is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.90,0:34:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rE}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.19,0:34:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们不认识的人\N{\rE}Oh, it's no one we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.45,0:34:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是炸弹吗 没什么特别的\N{\rE}Is that what I think it is? Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.91,0:34:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,钚制核心而已\N{\rE}Plutonium core.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.08,0:35:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大概相当于五六百万吨当量的炸药\N{\rE}I'm guessing a five or six megaton yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.33,0:35:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,足以把这整座城市炸得连渣都不剩\N{\rE}Enough to turn this entire city into a glass ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.21,0:35:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这\N{\rE}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.08,0:35:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不太妙啊\N{\rE}not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.17,0:35:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别费力气了 打不开\N{\rE}Already tried. Can't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.43,0:35:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看出来了\N{\rE}I see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.51,0:35:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔拿走了病毒闪存\N{\rE}Gabriel has the poison pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.89,0:35:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你或许想去找他\N{\rE}You might want to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.43,0:35:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会去的 你能解除炸弹吗\N{\rE}Yeah, we will. Can you disarm that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.52,0:35:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要阻止这九个引爆器发生内爆 以免引爆核心\N{\rE}I just have to stop these nine detonators from imploding the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.06,0:35:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拆下一个引爆器 就不会发生内爆\N{\rE}Detach one detonator, no implosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.36,0:35:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没有内爆 就达不到临界质量\N{\rE}And no implosion, no critical mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.57,0:35:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,达不到临界质量 也就达不到爆炸条件\N{\rE}And no critical mass, no six megaton blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.86,0:35:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还有多少时间 足够让你离开这里了\N{\rE}How much time we have? Enough time for you to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.08,0:35:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我用这些工具就能把铰链弄下来\N{\rE}Maybe with those tools I get these hinges off.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.08,0:35:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,即使你能把门打开\N{\rE}Even if you could get that gate open,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.46,0:35:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是需要把引爆器拆掉才行\N{\rE}I still have to detach one detonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.29,0:35:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\rE}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.96,0:35:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以拯救这座城市\N{\rE}I can save the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.30,0:36:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是整个隧道网络都要面临坍塌的风险\N{\rE}but this entire network of tunnels is going to cave in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.56,0:36:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是谁拆除引爆器\N{\rE}Whoever detaches that detonator...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.98,0:36:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,都难逃一死\N{\rE}is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.74,0:36:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都选择处理自己擅长的部分\N{\rE}We're both on the right side of that gate
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.91,0:36:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你很清楚这一点\N{\rE}and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.87,0:36:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,卢瑟 把工具包扔给我\N{\rE}Luther, throw me the tool bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.37,0:36:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,工具留在这儿自然有它的道理 伊森 你知道原因\N{\rE}They weren't left here by accident, Ethan. You know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.04,0:36:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔要留我活口\N{\rE}Gabriel needs me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.76,0:36:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而他想要你死\N{\rE}And he needs you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.88,0:36:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因为只有你可以再做一个病毒闪存\N{\rE}Because you are the only one who can make another poison pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.72,0:36:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也只有我可以找到那艘潜艇\N{\rE}And I am the only one who can get to that submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.56,0:36:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉伊森\N{\rE}Tell Ethan...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.47,0:36:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我会等着他的\N{\rE}I'll be waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.02,0:36:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他拿到病毒闪存\N{\rE}If he has the poison pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.69,0:36:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须把马蹄铁交给他\N{\rE}I have to bring him the Podkova
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.15,0:36:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这样他就能控制智体\N{\rE}so he can control the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.65,0:37:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你只能帮我到这儿了\N{\rE}This is where you leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.87,0:37:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,卢瑟\N{\rE}Luther.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.70,0:37:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们原本的计划呢\N{\rE}What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.21,0:37:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,退休\N{\rE}Retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.42,0:37:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,钓钓鱼\N{\rE}Go fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.88,0:37:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的任务\N{\rE}This is my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.71,0:37:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我注定要完成的工作\N{\rE}This is what I was born to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.76,0:37:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,卢瑟 不行 我做不到\N{\rE}Luther, I can't. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.18,0:37:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用再多说了 兄弟\N{\rE}There's nothing you need to say, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.89,0:37:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我清楚\N{\rE}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.89,0:37:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我都清楚\N{\rE}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.06,0:37:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我要走的路\N{\rE}I'm right where I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.15,0:37:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 你得赶紧走了\N{\rE}Ethan... you need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.32,0:37:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\rE}You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.03,0:37:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,找到盖布瑞尔\N{\rE}Find Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.75,0:37:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,卢瑟\N{\rE}Luther.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.82,0:37:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止他\N{\rE}Stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.74,0:37:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,为不曾谋面之人\N{\rE}For those we never meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.71,0:37:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为不曾谋面之人\N{\rE}For those we never meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.40,0:38:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔 你这个混蛋\N{\rE}Gabriel, you son of a bitch,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.66,0:38:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,休想逃出"电脑克星"的手掌心\N{\rE}no one is safe from Phineas Phreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.71,0:40:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我兄弟 德加\N{\rE}My man Degas.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.84,0:40:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了吗\N{\rE}Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.34,0:40:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他还活着\N{\rE}No, he's- he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.68,0:40:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是布里格斯 对不对\N{\rE}Briggs, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.93,0:40:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但布里格斯不是你的真名\N{\rE}But that isn't your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.94,0:40:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎么样\N{\rE}What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.69,0:40:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的真名是吉姆·菲尔普斯\N{\rE}Your real name is Jim Phelps.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.48,0:40:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你父亲一样\N{\rE}Like your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.28,0:40:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是个特工\N{\rE}He was in the service, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.70,0:40:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你七岁时他失踪了\N{\rE}He vanished when you were seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.83,0:40:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你当特工是为了查明他到底怎么了\N{\rE}You joined to find out what happened to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.91,0:40:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,后来你发现他犯了法\N{\rE}and you found out he had legal trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.96,0:40:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时有两个选择\N{\rE}He was offered the choice:
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.30,0:40:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,加入碟中谍小组\N{\rE}To join the IMF...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.21,0:40:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,或是在监狱里过完下半辈子\N{\rE}or spend the rest of his life in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.80,0:40:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你一样 亨特\N{\rE}Just like you, Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.09,0:40:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,区别就在于 你当时的罪名是谋杀 对不对\N{\rE}Only in your case, the charge was murder, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.85,0:40:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我猜\N{\rE}But let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.35,0:41:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你是冤枉的\N{\rE}You were framed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.39,0:41:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就像多年前 你说自己在布拉格是被陷害的一样\N{\rE}Just like your claim you were framed all those years ago in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.27,0:41:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,任务是怎么失败的\N{\rE}How the mission went sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.94,0:41:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的团队是怎么全军覆没的\N{\rE}How you lost your whole team.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.03,0:41:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你的说法让我父亲变成了叛徒\N{\rE}Your story had my father down as a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.87,0:41:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你杀了他\N{\rE}That's why you killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.25,0:41:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的 我也不希望变成这样\N{\rE}It's true. I wish it weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.17,0:41:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我还很介怀吗\N{\rE}You think I'm carrying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.42,0:41:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,以为我是来复仇的\N{\rE}That I'm here for revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.26,0:41:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还是 怎么\N{\rE}Or... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.22,0:41:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,以为我要替父正名\N{\rE}To clear my father's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.60,0:41:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如今我继承了这个名字\N{\rE}It's my name now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.02,0:41:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rE}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.27,0:41:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这里\N{\rE}I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.06,0:41:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道\N{\rE}because I know you're the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.86,0:41:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,导致世界末日的罪魁祸首就是你\N{\rE}the world's staring down the barrel at Armageddon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.44,0:41:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我也知道\N{\rE}And I also know it's not the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.69,0:41:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你第一次拿全人类的命运当赌注了\N{\rE}you've gambled with the fate of the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.20,0:41:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但凡你听从过一次命令\N{\rE}And none of that would matter to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.79,0:42:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,原本这一切\N{\rE}if you'd ever once
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.87,0:42:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不需要\N{\rE}been following
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.46,0:42:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,再操心\N{\rE}orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.63,0:42:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,布里格斯\N{\rE}Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.54,0:42:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔普斯\N{\rE}Phelps.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.80,0:42:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\rE}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.92,0:42:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,智体想让你对我心怀仇恨\N{\rE}The Entity wants you to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.09,0:42:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你正中下怀\N{\rE}It's counting on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.01,0:42:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,打败它的唯一方法\N{\rE}And the only way to beat it is to do the one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.31,0:42:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就是出其不意 做出意想不到的事情\N{\rE}it would never expect us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.23,0:42:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,会是什么\N{\rE}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.49,0:42:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了我了解你 亨特\N{\rE}You forget I know you, Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.66,0:42:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我对碟中谍小组的那一套也很清楚\N{\rE}I know all your IMF mind games.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.12,0:42:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等一切结束了 等你被吃干抹净\N{\rE}When this is over, when they're done with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.21,0:42:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\rE}you and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.67,0:42:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都逃不过清算\N{\rE}we'll have our reckoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.01,0:42:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友的事真是遗憾\N{\rE}It's a shame about your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.26,0:43:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,话又说回来\N{\rE}Then again,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.89,0:43:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你已经习惯了\N{\rE}you're used to losing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.14,0:43:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拉瑟山\N{\rE}美国弗吉尼亚州\N{\rE}紧急指挥中心
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.38,0:43:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\rE}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.31,0:43:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在你未经批准擅自执行外勤任务期间\N{\rE}While you've been out conducting your own personal field operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.77,0:43:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,智体已经袭击了多个国家的核指挥中心\N{\rE}the Entity has infiltrated the nuclear command centers of India,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.86,0:43:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,包括印度 以色列 巴基斯坦以及朝鲜\N{\rE}Israel, Pakistan, and North Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.28,0:43:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 就在凌晨四点的时候\N{\rE}Today at 0400 hours Zulu time,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.70,0:44:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,法国上游战略与生存网络设施遭到入侵\N{\rE}France's RAMSES facility was breached.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.62,0:44:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,法国的整个核武器库 现在都已经在智体的操纵和控制之下\N{\rE}Their entire nuclear arsenal is now under the Entity's command and control.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.58,0:44:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩四个国家的核武器库目前没受到威胁\N{\rE}That leaves only four nations with secure nuclear arsenals.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.71,0:44:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,英国 中国 俄罗斯 还有我们\N{\rE}U.K., China, Russia and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.60,0:44:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前经历的一切\N{\rE}Everything you were,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.27,0:44:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的所有事情\N{\rE}everything you've done
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.27,0:44:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,造成了今天的局面\N{\rE}has come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.28,0:44:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,三级防御状态
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.50,0:44:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拉伯海 北太平洋
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.36,0:45:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,乔治·H·W·布什号航空母舰 CVN 77
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.62,0:46:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,中情局黑色保险库盗窃案\N{\rE}The CIA Black Vault break-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.66,0:46:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 什么是"秘密特工名单"\N{\rE}I'm sorry, what is a "NOC list"?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.67,0:46:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有我们海外秘密特工的完整行动记录\N{\rE}A complete record of our covert operatives overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.67,0:46:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说这个人他\N{\rE}So this is the man who--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.84,0:46:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,闯入了我们自己的黑色保险库\N{\rE}Broke into our own Black Vault
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.68,0:46:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,偷了我们自己的间谍名单\N{\rE}and stole the list of our own spies, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.51,0:46:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,名单他确实也归还了\N{\rE}He did return the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.97,0:46:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,下一页里面写了\N{\rE}It's on the next page.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.73,0:46:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我该不会看错了吧 还有克里姆林宫爆炸案吗\N{\rE}Am I reading this correctly? The Kremlin bombing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.40,0:46:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,平心而论 那颗炸弹原本是想炸死他的\N{\rE}In fairness, the bomb was actually meant to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.57,0:46:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在一次国家情报指挥部的\N{\rE}He gassed a security briefing
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.70,0:46:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,安全简报会上 他施放了毒气\N{\rE}at the National Intelligence Directorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.45,0:46:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还只是两个月前的事\N{\rE}That was just two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.33,0:46:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩本来也要开这个会\N{\rE}You two would have been in that meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.92,0:46:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他易容成基特里奇先生助理的样子去参会\N{\rE}He arrived in the form of Mister Kittridge's aide.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.59,0:47:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,又乔装成基特里奇先生脱身 应该是这样\N{\rE}And left as Mister Kittridge, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.43,0:47:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么要把他铐起来\N{\rE}This explains the handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.26,0:47:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么他会出现在这儿\N{\rE}It's still not clear why he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.30,0:47:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,无论怎么样 眼前这个人我们只能靠他最后一搏\N{\rE}Like it or not, what we're looking at is our means of last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.89,0:47:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他也可能是我们避免核战争的唯一希望\N{\rE}Quite possibly our only hope of averting nuclear Armageddon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.52,0:47:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们想控制智体的话\N{\rE}If we want to control the Entity,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.98,0:47:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就必须跟他打交道\N{\rE}we have to deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.77,0:47:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他选择接受任务\N{\rE}Should he choose to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.08,0:47:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,亨特探员\N{\rE}Agent Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.96,0:47:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 你朋友的事请节哀\N{\rE}Madam President. I'm sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.47,0:47:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\rE}Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.27,0:48:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,说来听听吧\N{\rE}Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.65,0:48:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要那把钥匙 还要借一艘船\N{\rE}I need that key and the use of a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.65,0:48:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,具体一点是要一艘航母\N{\rE}Specifically, an aircraft carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.53,0:48:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果再具体一点 就是乔治·H·W·布什号\N{\rE}More specifically, the George H.W. Bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.08,0:48:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他居然要"借"\N{\rE}He wants the "use of"
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.33,0:48:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是价值65亿美元的核动力军事资产\N{\rE}a six-and-a-half billion dollar nuclear-powered military asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.21,0:48:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,并且要向舰长下达命令 让他全力配合满足我的一切要求\N{\rE}With instructions for the ship's commander to accommodate my every request.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.84,0:48:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,具体要做什么呢\N{\rE}To do what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.34,0:48:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,用那把钥匙和钥匙能开启的东西\N{\rE}Use that key and what it opens
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.30,0:48:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,去除掉智体\N{\rE}to kill the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.97,0:48:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,除掉智体意味着网络空间会被彻底摧毁\N{\rE}Killing the Entity means the annihilation of cyberspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.14,0:48:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那样就会带来灾难性的后果\N{\rE}The consequences of which are catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.64,0:48:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我凭什么要听你的建议\N{\rE}Why the hell would I do what you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.14,0:48:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请恕我直言总统女士 您别无选择\N{\rE}Respectfully, Madam President, you have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.40,0:48:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,办法和选择总是会有的 不 女士\N{\rE}There is always another choice. No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.90,0:48:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,眼下来看 没有别的办法\N{\rE}In this case, not a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.07,0:48:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上的核大国 开始互相猜疑心生芥蒂\N{\rE}The world's nuclear powers are in a paranoid downward spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.78,0:48:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,各国本来都有机会不使用核导弹 不过\N{\rE}Every nation had a chance to take their missiles offline,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.95,0:48:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都不信任彼此\N{\rE}but no one trusted anyone else to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.41,0:48:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,国务院也在提醒您 各种外交渠道也正在面临崩塌\N{\rE}Your State Department is warning you that diplomatic channels are breaking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.00,0:49:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,掌控核武器库的各国都在考 虑率先发动攻击\N{\rE}Everyone who still has control of their arsenals is considering a first strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.17,0:49:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就像您一样\N{\rE}Just like you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.59,0:49:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,情报也清楚表明 智体正在不断学习\N{\rE}The intelligence community knows that the Entity is learning as it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.67,0:49:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它会变得越来越聪明 越来越强大\N{\rE}It's getting smarter, it's getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.93,0:49:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也只有72个小时的时间\N{\rE}They know that we have only 72 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.14,0:49:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,时间一过 地球上所有核武器库都会被智体掌控\N{\rE}before every other nuclear arsenal on Earth is under the Entity's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.68,0:49:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,三天后 地球上最坚固最安全的防御系统\N{\rE}Three days before it focuses the full force of its energy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.73,0:49:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是我们的防御系统会遭受猛烈攻击\N{\rE}on the toughest, most secure defense system on the planet: Ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.85,0:49:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,到那个时候 国防部将别无选择\N{\rE}At which point, the Defense Department will have no choice but to insist
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.44,0:49:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只能坚持要求您打开那个箱子\N{\rE}that you open that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.11,0:49:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,并输入密码 先发制人\N{\rE}enter the codes, and launch an all-out preemptive strike
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.32,0:49:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,赶在智体控制我们的核武器之前\N{\rE}on the world's eight other nuclear arsenals
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.28,0:49:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击世界上其他八个核武器库\N{\rE}before the Entity takes control of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.16,0:49:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士\N{\rE}Madam President,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.66,0:49:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,毁灭世界的不是您就会是智体\N{\rE}either you destroy the world or the Entity does.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.04,0:49:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 都注定没有胜算\N{\rE}In any case, it is checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.71,0:49:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还有别的选择\N{\rE}There is another choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.29,0:49:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把钥匙的秘密告诉我\N{\rE}You could tell me what you know about that key
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.13,0:49:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们有能力可以控制智体\N{\rE}and give us the power to control the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.42,0:49:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 要是可以的话 我早就把一切都告诉您了\N{\rE}Madam President, if I believed that were true, I would tell you everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.13,0:49:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无保留\N{\rE}Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.05,0:49:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,您掌管过中情局 您面临心理战的时候也知道是怎么回事\N{\rE}You ran the CIA, you know psychological warfare when you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.93,0:49:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,您就看看周围吧\N{\rE}Just look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.60,0:50:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们身处智体构造的现实中\N{\rE}We are in the Entity's reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.23,0:50:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信它正巴不得您来阻止我\N{\rE}And I believe it's counting on you to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.94,0:50:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你说的是真的\N{\rE}If what you're saying is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.94,0:50:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你又怎么能确定 我们按你的建议行事\N{\rE}how can you be sure the Entity doesn't want us to do
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.07,0:50:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是中了智体下怀呢\N{\rE}exactly what you're proposing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.99,0:50:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,因为智体清楚 你们肯定会按逻辑行事\N{\rE}Because it knows you would never do anything so illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.61,0:50:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不会疯狂到相信我\N{\rE}That you would be insane to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.03,0:50:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你们才更应该相信我\N{\rE}And that is precisely why you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.78,0:50:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就这一次\N{\rE}For once,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.62,0:50:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,至于我们要怎么做 就让智体自己猜去吧\N{\rE}let's let the Entity worry about what we're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.75,0:50:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心的是另外三个国家\N{\rE}I'm worried about those three other nations, Madam President,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.66,0:50:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 他们仍然控制着自己的核武器库\N{\rE}still in control of their arsenals.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.46,0:50:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可能会乱了阵脚 可能因此发动全面进攻\N{\rE}Nations who could panic and launch a full-scale attack
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.17,0:50:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而他却带着一艘航母 在外面不知道要搞什么名堂\N{\rE}while he's out there with an aircraft carrier, doing God knows what!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.01,0:50:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他这一系列操作都是为了要除掉智体\N{\rE}While he's out there trying to kill the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.84,0:50:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道这不是明智的做法\N{\rE}Which we all know is a terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.26,0:50:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 求您了 请给我三天时间 同时\N{\rE}Madam President, please. I'm asking for three days while you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.64,0:50:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,请让世界冷静一下\N{\rE}keep the world calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.64,0:50:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,三天\N{\rE}Three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.94,0:50:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么时候\N{\rE}Have I ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.69,0:50:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,让您失望过\N{\rE}let you down before?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.23,0:50:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果智体决定提前发起攻击呢\N{\rE}And when the Entity decides to attack before then?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.40,0:50:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,它控制的核导弹能让数十亿人丧命 为什么它不动手\N{\rE}It has enough missiles to kill billions already. Why hasn't it done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.11,0:50:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它是一台机器\N{\rE}Because it's a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.99,0:50:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,思维跟机器一样 属于二进制 不 它的思维\N{\rE}It's thinking like a machine. No, its thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.32,0:50:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,思维来自于它从我们身上学到的经验\N{\rE}Its thinking is binary... is dictated by what it's learned from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.83,0:51:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它没发起攻击是因为它还没完全控制\N{\rE}It hasn't launched because it doesn't have total control.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.29,0:51:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,它需要控制全世界的核武器库 才能保证获得它期望的结果\N{\rE}It needs the world's entire atomic arsenal to guarantee the desired outcome:
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.96,0:51:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,它想要彻底消灭人类\N{\rE}The total annihilation of humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.96,0:51:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士\N{\rE}Madam President,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.55,0:51:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它是在静待时机\N{\rE}it is going to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.24,0:51:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,英国
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.16,0:51:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,英国离线
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.20,0:51:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,位于伦敦的诺斯伍德核行动和目标中心遭到入侵\N{\rE}Northwood Nuclear Operations and Targeting Centre in London has been breached.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.87,0:51:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,英国失去了对核武器库的控制权\N{\rE}The United Kingdom has lost control of its arsenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.75,0:51:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我最后再问你一次\N{\rE}I will ask you one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.17,0:51:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这把钥匙能打开什么\N{\rE}What does this unlock?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.75,0:51:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,埃丽卡\N{\rE}Erika,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.96,0:51:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你相信我\N{\rE}I need you to trust me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.92,0:51:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,信我这一次\N{\rE}one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.01,0:51:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你给我听好了\N{\rE}Trust me when I tell you:
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.64,0:52:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等到72小时倒计时结束之后\N{\rE}When that clock runs out in 72 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.52,0:52:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我会立马按下那个按钮\N{\rE}I will press that button,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.35,0:52:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,到那个时候 一切后果都由你承担\N{\rE}and that will be your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.60,0:52:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士\N{\rE}Madam President--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.36,0:52:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,中士们\N{\rE}Sergeants,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.69,0:52:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,把他关起来\N{\rE}lock him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.30,0:52:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,总统的话你都听见了\N{\rE}You heard the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.55,0:52:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你有72个小时\N{\rE}You have 72 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.22,0:52:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她说等时机成熟 你自然知道怎么使用它\N{\rE}She says you'll know what to do with this when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.11,0:52:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\rE}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.82,0:52:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\rE}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.75,0:53:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你留了一条信息 等一切结束了再看\N{\rE}I left you a message on there for when this is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.08,0:53:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.10,0:53:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,或者到时候 你亲口\N{\rE}You can tell me yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.14,0:53:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\rE}after.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.19,0:53:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,选择当特工的时候 我们大家都宣过誓\N{\rE}They made us take an oath when they gave us the choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.44,0:53:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,无论生死皆隐于世\N{\rE}We live and die in the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.90,0:53:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只为我们珍爱之人\N{\rE}for those we hold close...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.20,0:53:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也为不曾谋面之人\N{\rE}and for those we never meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.95,0:53:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你在想什么\N{\rE}I know what's on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.62,0:53:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时留着钥匙 你做得没错\N{\rE}You did the right thing when you kept the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.29,0:53:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都站在正义的一方 兄弟\N{\rE}You've always been on the right side, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.46,0:53:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是\N{\rE}Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.88,0:53:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别忘记\N{\rE}Never forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.88,0:54:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的人生不是单凭某个行为而决定的\N{\rE}our lives are not defined by any one action.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.30,0:54:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的人生\N{\rE}Our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.56,0:54:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是各种选择相加的结果\N{\rE}are the sum of our choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.18,0:54:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有什么遗憾\N{\rE}I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.23,0:54:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你也应该不要有\N{\rE}Neither should you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.40,0:54:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,航空母舰第十战斗群\N{\rE}北太平洋某处
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.76,0:55:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,C.尼丽\N{\rE}第十战斗群指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.46,0:55:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,1996年5月22日
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.86,0:55:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,埃丽卡她\N{\rE}Did Erika--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.19,0:55:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,总统有没有\N{\rE}Did the President
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.49,0:55:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你这张纸条背后的含义\N{\rE}tell you the meaning behind this note?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.03,0:55:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 长官\N{\rE}No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.66,0:55:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,塞尔维亚 1996年5月22日\N{\rE}Serbia. May 22nd, 1996.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.54,0:55:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两个都失去了自己的珍爱之人\N{\rE}We both lost someone we loved. Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.71,0:55:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为当时的掌权者不愿冒险\N{\rE}All because no one in authority would take a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.79,0:56:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在也是如履薄冰 先生\N{\rE}I'm sitting on a powder keg, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.21,0:56:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,近在眼前的那艘正是俄罗斯唯一的航母 库兹涅佐夫上将号\N{\rE}Just over that horizon is Russia's only aircraft carrier, the Admiral Kuznetsov.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.93,0:56:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只要走错一步 我就会制造二战以来\N{\rE}I am one wrong move away from the first shoot-out
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.18,0:56:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,两艘航母间的首次交火\N{\rE}between two flattops since World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.47,0:56:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,稍有不慎 就会触发第三次世界大战\N{\rE}One flinch from touching off World War III.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.73,0:56:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而你竟然主动要我把你往火坑里送\N{\rE}And you're asking me to fly you directly into the eye of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.28,0:56:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官 让我去\N{\rE}Yes, ma'am, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.49,0:56:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在找什么东西\N{\rE}What exactly are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.36,0:56:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,声监系统\N{\rE}SOSUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.82,0:56:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,全称叫"声呐监听系统"\N{\rE}Short for "Sound Surveillance System."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.20,0:56:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,遍布全球的海底声波线缆网络\N{\rE}It's a worldwide network of undersea acoustic cables
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.37,0:56:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可以追溯到冷战时期\N{\rE}dating back to the Cold War.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.41,0:56:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在世界各个地方发生的所有重大海底事件\N{\rE}If an undersea event of any significance happens anywhere in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.96,0:56:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,都能被任意一座监听基站定位 可以精确到平方米\N{\rE}one of these listening stations will pinpoint that event to the square meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.13,0:56:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一座监听基站\N{\rE}And one of these SOSUS stations
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.80,0:56:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定记录了失踪的俄罗斯潜艇\N{\rE}will have recorded our missing Russian submarine's
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.80,0:56:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在2012年冬天撞击海床的事件\N{\rE}impact on the sea floor in the winter of 2012.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.30,0:56:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,却完全没发现这次事件到底有多么重要\N{\rE}Without ever understanding the significance of the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.64,0:56:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而俄国人知道塞瓦斯托波尔号的失踪时间\N{\rE}Whereas the Russians know when the Sevastopol vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.18,0:56:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是不确定具体地点\N{\rE}They're just not exactly sure where.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.40,0:56:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]我们必须做出选择\N{\rE}[In French]We must make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.05,0:57:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]对 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.48,0:57:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多基站\N{\rE}Which one
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.06,0:57:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,到底哪一座 记录了这次事件呢\N{\rE}out of all these SOSUS stations picked up the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.99,0:57:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,塞瓦斯托波尔号潜艇官兵的尸体已被发现\N{\rE}We know the bodies of the Sevastopol's crew were recovered in sea ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.03,0:57:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就在海上的浮冰中 尸体是被因纽特渔民发现的\N{\rE}And since they were recovered by Inuit fishermen...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.82,0:57:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们猜测沉没地点在北极某处\N{\rE}We're guessing it went down somewhere in the Arctic.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.04,0:57:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,搜索面积大约是1400万平方公里\N{\rE}A search area of roughly five and a half million square miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.54,0:57:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 最有可能记录到信号的声呐监听基站是\N{\rE}Meaning the most likely SOSUS station to pick it up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.04,0:57:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这一座 在白令海\N{\rE}This one. In the Bering Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.84,0:57:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,圣马修岛\N{\rE}St. Matthew Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.38,0:57:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,俄国人会发现的\N{\rE}The Russians will know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.47,0:57:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么还没有直接突袭这座岛\N{\rE}Why haven't they just stormed the island already?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.38,0:57:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,因为圣马修岛属于美国政府管辖\N{\rE}Because St. Matthew is a U.S. Government installation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.89,0:57:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,公开的侵略行为会引发第三次世界大战\N{\rE}An overt act of aggression would trigger World War III.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.10,0:57:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在世界末日就要来了\N{\rE}But now Armageddon is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.78,0:57:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]俄罗斯人也已经豁出去了\N{\rE}[in French]And the Russians have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.02,0:57:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友知道他们即将卷入一场包围战吗\N{\rE}Do your friends know they're walking into a potential siege?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.77,0:57:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道这是任务\N{\rE}They know that's the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.86,0:57:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 要从塞瓦斯托波尔号取回智体的源代码\N{\rE}So, to retrieve the Entity's source code from Sevastopol,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.11,0:57:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森要知道圣马修岛记录的精确坐标\N{\rE}Ethan needs the precise coordinates from St. Matthew Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.20,0:57:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,显然还需要一艘潜艇\N{\rE}And a submarine, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.41,0:57:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,潜艇还得可以带你去你想去的地方\N{\rE}One that's willing to take you where you want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.04,0:58:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不提出任何质疑\N{\rE}No questions asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.54,0:58:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\rE}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.92,0:58:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还要假设你的朋友真的能拿到坐标\N{\rE}And that's assuming your friends can actually get the coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.54,0:58:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们预计每两小时发送一次坐标位置 每次持续15分钟\N{\rE}Which we're expected to transmit for fifteen minutes every two hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.22,0:58:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,希望伊森到时候能设法接收到我们的信号\N{\rE}In the hope that Ethan is somehow able to receive our signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.80,0:58:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么从冰层下面逃出来\N{\rE}How do you intend to make it out from under the ice cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.64,0:58:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把坐标发给我之后 我的队员就会赶过去\N{\rE}After sending me the coordinates, my team will make their way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.43,0:58:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森会带上特高频发射器\N{\rE}Now, Ethan will have a VHF transmitter
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.60,0:58:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们就可以定位他在冰下的确切位置\N{\rE}which will enable us to zero in on his exact location under the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.98,0:58:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的下一步就是拿起电锯 然后\N{\rE}All we have to do then is grab a chainsaw and--
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.65,0:58:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 要在冰层上开个窟窿 把伊森拽出来吗\N{\rE}What? Cut a hole in the ice cap and just pull Ethan out?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.41,0:58:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 根据潜艇残骸所在的深度\N{\rE}Hang on. Depending on how deep that wreck is,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.99,0:58:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没等伊森上浮到水面 就会出现严重的减压病症状\N{\rE}Ethan will have severe decompression sickness before he reaches the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.54,0:58:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,正因如此 我们准备了这个\N{\rE}Which is why we have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.63,0:58:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,充气式高压减压舱
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.37,0:58:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么东西\N{\rE}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.42,0:58:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这个东西是 目前最先进的充气式高压减压舱\N{\rE}This is a state-of-the-art inflatable hyperbaric decompression chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.42,0:58:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你没开玩笑吧\N{\rE}You're not serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.59,0:58:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 你是想告诉我 伊森的性命\N{\rE}What? You mean to tell me that Ethan's life
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.68,0:58:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,以及地球上所有生物的命运\N{\rE}and the fate of all life on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.93,0:59:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就全在于我们能不能在同一时间\N{\rE}depends on us all meeting at the exact same place
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.35,0:59:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,赶到结冰的白令海\N{\rE}at the exact same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.81,0:59:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,并且精准地在同一个位置碰头\N{\rE}somewhere in the frozen Bering Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.03,0:59:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还要带着这个\N{\rE}with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.11,0:59:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rE}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.49,0:59:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我们还没赶到 他就溺水了呢\N{\rE}And what if he drowns before we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.74,0:59:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,按理来说 有可能\N{\rE}In all likelihood, he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.95,0:59:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那里的海水很冷 体温过低会降低新陈代谢速度\N{\rE}But in water that cold, the hypothermia will slow down his metabolic functions
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.33,0:59:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可以给我们解救他争取时间\N{\rE}and buy us time to revive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.83,0:59:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你的计划吗\N{\rE}That's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.71,0:59:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rE}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.79,0:59:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的计划\N{\rE}That's our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.20,0:59:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,1996年5月22日
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.80,0:59:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个范围内的潜艇只有俄亥俄号\N{\rE}The only submarine in range is the Ohio.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.22,0:59:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,艇长是杰克·布莱索\N{\rE}Jack Bledsoe's boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.14,0:59:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,潜艇下潜的时候\N{\rE}When submerged,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.35,0:59:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只能通过超低频无线电联系他 数字传输信号都会被屏蔽\N{\rE}he's reachable only by VLF radio- shielded from any digital transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.81,0:59:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这也就说明他对智体免疫\N{\rE}That means he is immune to this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.98,0:59:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但前提是他得保持潜水状态\N{\rE}But only if he stays submerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.36,0:59:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼鹰飞机可以在两小时内送你过去 但它燃料有限不能久留\N{\rE}An Osprey can get you there in two hours, but it won't have enough fuel to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.57,0:59:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也没别的办法了\N{\rE}There's no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.24,1:00:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果布莱索艇长收到我的命令\N{\rE}If Bledsoe receives my command,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.45,1:00:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他相信这一切是真的\N{\rE}if he believes it to be authentic,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.12,1:00:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能会上浮到潜望镜深度\N{\rE}he might come to periscope depth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.87,1:00:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能会等待30秒\N{\rE}He might wait thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.33,1:00:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕你只是迟到一分钟的话\N{\rE}If you are even one minute late...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.79,1:00:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我试一试吧\N{\rE}Just give me this chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.43,1:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,弗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.43,1:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,托
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.43,1:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,斯
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.43,1:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,里
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.43,1:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,克
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.43,1:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.43,1:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,保
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.43,1:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,佑
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.43,1:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.43,1:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,们
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.09,1:00:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,风速稳定在15节 甲板已做清理
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.89,1:00:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,最终检查完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.42,1:00:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你放亨特走了\N{\rE}You let Hunt go?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.54,1:00:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才已经说了 钥匙也拿走了\N{\rE}That's what I said. With the key?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.59,1:00:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没有钥匙 他什么都做不了 那他现在在哪里\N{\rE}He couldn't do much without it. So where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.30,1:00:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜应该是在北太平洋某个地方吧\N{\rE}Somewhere in the Northern Pacific, I assume.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.63,1:01:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你给了他一艘航空母舰\N{\rE}You gave him an aircraft carrier?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.39,1:01:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我是武装部队的总司令 部长先生\N{\rE}I am the Commander in Chief of the Armed Forces, Mister Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.06,1:01:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的航空母舰\N{\rE}It is my aircraft carrier
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.39,1:01:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想怎么安排都可以\N{\rE}and I do with it as I please.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.94,1:01:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你早就知道会发生这种事\N{\rE}You knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.02,1:01:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我原本只是怀疑\N{\rE}I suspected.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.27,1:01:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你至少应该通知我们一下\N{\rE}You could have at least told us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.78,1:01:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚说了 现在你们可以去忙了\N{\rE}I just did. And now you're excused.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.11,1:01:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 就先这样吧\N{\rE}Madam President- That will be all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.75,1:01:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我没能告诉你\N{\rE}I couldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.21,1:01:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事必须由我自己亲自负责\N{\rE}It had to be my responsibility and mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.93,1:01:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我得为亨特争取时间\N{\rE}And I had to buy Hunt time.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.22,1:01:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有人要试图阻止他\N{\rE}Someone could have tried to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.31,1:01:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可能不同意你的做法 但是确实尊重你的权威\N{\rE}They may not agree with you, but they do respect your authority.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.93,1:01:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,事情没结束之前 有人会惊慌\N{\rE}Before this is over, someone will panic.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.56,1:01:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,也有人会试图出来阻止我\N{\rE}Someone will try to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.35,1:01:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,2天13小时29分钟
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.78,1:02:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,又是一次实地考察\N{\rE}Another field trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.91,1:02:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他在哪儿吗 你知道他最后去哪儿\N{\rE}You know where he's at? I know where he's gonna end up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.29,1:02:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们给他个惊喜\N{\rE}Let's surprise him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.61,1:02:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,圣马修岛\N{\rE}白令海
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.02,1:02:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,千万记住 关于塞瓦斯托波尔号\N{\rE}Now remember, governments would kill
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.86,1:02:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,政府会想办法探我们的底\N{\rE}to know what we know about the Sevastopol.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.02,1:02:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是中情局站点\N{\rE}This is a CIA station
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.23,1:02:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这里全都是老练的外勤特工\N{\rE}run by seasoned field agents trained
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.13,1:02:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们经过信息采集训练 要加倍小心\N{\rE}to get information and never, ever give it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.91,1:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,任务内容一个字都不能透露 交涉的事交给我来处理\N{\rE}Tell them nothing about our real mission. Just let me do the talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.53,1:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.29,1:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]是谁来了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.83,1:03:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]咱们来客人了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.73,1:03:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rE}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.40,1:03:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要帮忙吗 那真是太好了 需要\N{\rE}Can I help you? I certainly hope so. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.90,1:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在正在找声呐监听基站\N{\rE}We're looking for the SOSUS listening station.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.57,1:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是 朋友 我是站长 我叫比尔·多诺利\N{\rE}You found it, friend. I'm the station chief, Bill Donloe.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.86,1:03:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我妻子 塔蓓萨\N{\rE}My wife, Tapeesa.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.70,1:03:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 真是幸会\N{\rE}Hello. How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.20,1:03:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 比尔\N{\rE}Well, nice to meet you, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.24,1:03:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是研究员 来自英国地震学\N{\rE}We're researchers from the British Seismological--
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.70,1:03:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你说的是多诺利吗\N{\rE}I'm sorry, did you say Donloe?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.54,1:03:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 比尔\N{\rE}That's right. Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.96,1:03:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉·多诺利\N{\rE}William Donloe?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.96,1:03:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在兰利的多诺利 黑色保险库的多诺利\N{\rE}Langley Donloe? Black Vault Donloe?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.55,1:03:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是同一个人\N{\rE}The same.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.00,1:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,请问你是\N{\rE}And you are?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.34,1:03:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真没想到 不会吧\N{\rE}I don't believe... Are you ser...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.97,1:03:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙是个传奇程序员\N{\rE}This guy is a coding legend.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.55,1:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他在兰利设计了中情局的主机 黑色保险库\N{\rE}He designed the CIA mainframe at Langley. The Black Vault.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.26,1:03:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是地球上最安全的数据库 没人能黑得进去\N{\rE}It's the most secure database on the planet. It's completely impenetrable.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.23,1:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要真有那么神 我就不会在这儿了\N{\rE}Well, if it were impenetrable, I wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.52,1:03:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,保险库在1996年被黑过\N{\rE}The Vault was breached in '96
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.06,1:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,中情局当天就把我下放了\N{\rE}and the agency shipped me out the same day.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.28,1:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,后来一直待在这里\N{\rE}Been here ever since.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.07,1:04:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 所以 也就是说 你在这个岛上待了\N{\rE}Wait. So you mean to say you've been on this island for...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.57,1:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,30年了\N{\rE}Thirty years.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.79,1:04:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常地好奇 你是怎么知道黑色保险库的\N{\rE}Just out of curiosity, how do you know about the Black Vault?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.66,1:04:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是高度机密\N{\rE}That's highly classified.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.58,1:04:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,滴答 滴答\N{\rE}Tick-tock, tick-tock, tick-tock.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.17,1:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你刚才说你们是谁\N{\rE}Sorry. Who did you say you were?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.42,1:04:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆告诉他我们的来意吧\N{\rE}Just tell the man why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.42,1:04:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,多诺利先生 比尔\N{\rE}Mr. Donloe. Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.67,1:04:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就算能告诉你实情 你也不会相信\N{\rE}Even if we could tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.26,1:04:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,换我也不信 格蕾丝\N{\rE}you wouldn't believe it. I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.93,1:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,关键是我们需要调取\N{\rE}The heart of the matter is that we need access
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.68,1:04:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,2012年晚冬以来的所有监听基站数据\N{\rE}to all your SOSUS data from late winter 2012.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.47,1:04:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,否则几天之内 世界将不复存在\N{\rE}Otherwise the world will cease to exist in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.10,1:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,已经开始了 对吗\N{\rE}It's happening, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.23,1:04:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那个智体\N{\rE}The Entity.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.11,1:04:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年我一直尝试提醒人们 但是\N{\rE}I've tried to warn people about it for years, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.99,1:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没人愿意听\N{\rE}no one would listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.53,1:04:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我们吗\N{\rE}Can you help us?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.70,1:04:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我也希望我可以\N{\rE}I wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.51,1:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,请进吧\N{\rE}Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.14,1:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,随意点 别客气\N{\rE}Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.86,1:05:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 醒醒\N{\rE}Sir! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.90,1:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒 长官\N{\rE}Wake up, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.65,1:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们遇到麻烦了 真正的大麻烦\N{\rE}We got problems. Real problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.49,1:05:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了 是库兹涅佐夫上将号\N{\rE}What's happening? It's the Admiral Kuznetsov.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.16,1:05:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得离开这里\N{\rE}We got to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.08,1:05:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们进入了俄国人的攻击范围\N{\rE}We're in Ivan's threat zone, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.45,1:05:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看见俄亥俄号了吗 没有 长官 飞机燃料不足\N{\rE}Any sign of the Ohio? No, sir. And we're at bingo.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.25,1:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不尽快掉头 燃料就不够返回航母了\N{\rE}If I don't turn around soon, we won't have enough fuel to get us back to the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.09,1:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,无线电消息呢 甚高频发射器一直没有反应\N{\rE}Anything on the radio? Nothing but static on VHF.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.55,1:05:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的朋友在发送信号 我们这儿没收到\N{\rE}If your friends are broadcasting a signal, we can't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.05,1:05:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,进入悬停状态\N{\rE}Just take us into a hover.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.30,1:05:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 飞机没油了 五分钟\N{\rE}Sir, we are at bingo. Five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.26,1:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就给我五分钟 拜托了\N{\rE}Just give me five minutes. Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.81,1:05:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,只给你一分钟\N{\rE}We can give you one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.48,1:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,减速\N{\rE}Decel.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.94,1:06:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要悬停 我们得赶紧撤离\N{\rE}What are we doing in a hover? We got to bug out!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.36,1:06:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,注意两点钟方向\N{\rE}Bogies at two.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.95,1:06:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们亮出了机载导弹\N{\rE}They're showing us their missiles, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.08,1:06:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只警告我们这一次\N{\rE}That's the only warning we're gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.12,1:06:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,俄罗斯战机请注意 我们是猎空号战机\N{\rE}Russian Aircraft...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.05,1:06:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这简直堪比三战爆发 快撤\N{\rE}This is some World War III shit here. We got to go!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.46,1:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在国际空域执行常规任务 没有任何敌意\N{\rE}International airspace. No challenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.21,1:06:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,重复一遍 我们没有任何敌意\N{\rE}I repeat: No challenge is intended.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.55,1:06:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里\N{\rE}Where the hell are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.07,1:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,2天11小时31分钟
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.54,1:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,中国
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.71,1:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里 伊森\N{\rE}Where are you, Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.33,1:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,美国潜艇\N{\rE}俄亥俄号\N{\rE}地点 机密
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.15,1:08:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定是布莱索艇长\N{\rE}You must be Captain Bledsoe.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.32,1:08:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那你一定是精神有问题\N{\rE}And you must be out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.95,1:08:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们没出现 你原本有什么计划\N{\rE}What exactly was the plan if we hadn't shown up?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.96,1:08:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 我也没有长远计划\N{\rE}You know, I really hadn't thought that far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.00,1:08:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rE}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.54,1:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\N{\rE}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.72,1:08:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,尼丽少将让我向你问好\N{\rE}Rear Admiral Neely sends her regards.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.18,1:08:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她跟我说会看到绿色信号弹\N{\rE}She told me to expect a green flare.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.10,1:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可她没说还要挨电击\N{\rE}She never mentioned a Taser.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.68,1:08:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可以告诉我是怎么回事吗\N{\rE}Mind telling me what this is all about?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.89,1:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的任务内容是机密\N{\rE}My mission is classified. Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.19,1:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你带我去北边\N{\rE}I need you to take me north.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.94,1:08:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\rE}Continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.53,1:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我在等一组精确的坐标定位\N{\rE}I'm expecting a set of exact coordinates
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.11,1:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,会通过摩尔斯密码传过来\N{\rE}via Morse code transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.95,1:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那你打算怎么在水下收到坐标信息呢\N{\rE}And just how exactly do you expect to receive them down here?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.28,1:09:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你得上升到潜望镜深度\N{\rE}You'd have to come to periscope depth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.16,1:09:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,架起天线\N{\rE}Raise the antenna.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.87,1:09:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对特高频电波的低频进行信号扫描\N{\rE}Signal-scan the low end of the VHF band.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.12,1:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,扫描多久 15分钟\N{\rE}For how long? Fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.96,1:09:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也就给了俄国人15分钟确定我们的位置\N{\rE}That would give the Russians fifteen minutes to pinpoint our location.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.05,1:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,从中午开始 之后每隔两小时扫描一次\N{\rE}Starting at noon, and every two hours after that,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.05,1:09:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我的队友 把坐标信息发给我\N{\rE}until my team sends me those coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.47,1:09:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,北边是白令海 先生\N{\rE}North is the Bering Sea, mister.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.43,1:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,俄罗斯太平洋舰队的每艘潜艇都在那里\N{\rE}Right now every submarine in the Russian Pacific Fleet is up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.02,1:09:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我的主要任务是确定他们的位置\N{\rE}My primary mission is to lock down their positions
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.48,1:09:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,并搞清楚他们要干什么\N{\rE}and ascertain what they're up to.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.40,1:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你应该知道答案\N{\rE}I'm thinking you know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.74,1:09:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么 那是圣马修岛\N{\rE}What is that? That's St. Matthew Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.07,1:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,岛上除了一个旧声呐监听基站什么也没有\N{\rE}There's nothing there but an old SOSUS listening station.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.58,1:09:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 它旁边的那个 是什么\N{\rE}No, no, that right next to it. What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.12,1:09:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那是洛沙里克号\N{\rE}That's the Losharik.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.79,1:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道它是干什么的\N{\rE}You know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.80,1:09:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,隶属俄罗斯特种部队的小型潜艇\N{\rE}It's a mini-sub, Russian Special Forces.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.30,1:10:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的一点也不错 先生\N{\rE}Get yourself a gold star, mister.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.30,1:10:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,空中侦察在一个多小时前 发现它出现在圣马修岛附近\N{\rE}Aerial recon spotted it off St. Matthew Island just over an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.35,1:10:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它从这里开始部署\N{\rE}It's deployed from this:
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.64,1:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别尔哥罗德号 俄罗斯海军攻击力最强的潜艇\N{\rE}The Belgorod. The deadliest submarine in the Russian Navy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.27,1:10:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我的附加任务就是找到这艘潜艇 让它处于攻击范围内\N{\rE}My secondary mission is to locate that bastard and hold it at risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.40,1:10:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,洛沙里克号的出现意味着它在附近\N{\rE}The Losharik means it's somewhere close by.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.49,1:10:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那座岛上有你的人手\N{\rE}You have people on that island.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.15,1:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你的坐标会从那里发出来\N{\rE}That's where your coordinates are coming from.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.66,1:10:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你会帮我吗\N{\rE}Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.62,1:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\rE}Mister...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.17,1:10:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想惹俄国人\N{\rE}if you want to poke the bear,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.46,1:10:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那你算是找对人了\N{\rE}oh, you've come to the right man.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.01,1:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟你的潜水长聊聊 长官\N{\rE}Like to speak with your divemaster, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.47,1:10:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,值班长\N{\rE}Chief!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.72,1:10:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官\N{\rE}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.26,1:10:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让皮尔斯到精锐侦察队分区待命\N{\rE}Have Pills meet our guest in the FORECON quarters.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.76,1:10:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官 您这边请\N{\rE}Aye, sir. This way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.67,1:10:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,圣马修岛
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.98,1:10:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟这里的朋友解释过了\N{\rE}As I've explained to our friends here,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.81,1:10:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有他们想要的数据\N{\rE}I don't have the data they want.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.90,1:11:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,十年来 中情局一直无视我提出的升级申请\N{\rE}The agency ignored my request to upgrade our system for a decade.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.03,1:11:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天 有一个小队 突然造访\N{\rE}One day a team shows up, unannounced,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.70,1:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,短短几天的时间 把整个系统都做了规划\N{\rE}and refits the entire system in a matter of days.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.49,1:11:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜那是在2012年的冬天\N{\rE}I'm guessing this is the winter of 2012.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.33,1:11:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 旧系统是靠磁带运行的\N{\rE}Right. The old system ran on magnetic tapes,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.95,1:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,备份到20厘米的软盘里面\N{\rE}backed up to 8-inch floppies.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.83,1:11:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,软盘存放在后面的狗棚\N{\rE}These were in the dog shed out back.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.33,1:11:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这些盒子里可能有你们要找的坐标信息\N{\rE}These boxes might contain the coordinates you're all looking for,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.88,1:11:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我没有读取器\N{\rE}but I don't have a reader.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.34,1:11:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,读取器被拿走了 也是2012年\N{\rE}That was also taken away in 2012.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.05,1:11:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你指望他做个读取器\N{\rE}You expect him to build one.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.22,1:11:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来找坐标的 不是找盒子的\N{\rE}I came for coordinates, not boxes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.35,1:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,假设你找到了坐标 我的队员会怎么样\N{\rE}Supposing you find the coordinates. What happens to my team?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.77,1:11:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把坐标信息汇报给我的上级 我的人在这里待命\N{\rE}I will take the coordinates to my superiors. My men wait here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.35,1:11:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们找到想要的东西\N{\rE}When we have located what we're looking for,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.23,1:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人就会离开 不会伤害你们\N{\rE}my men will leave and you will not be harmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.27,1:11:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要换做是你 你相信吗\N{\rE}Would you believe that if you were me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.48,1:11:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不信\N{\rE}No, I would not.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.74,1:11:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你有一小时来制作读取器\N{\rE}You have one hour to build the drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.24,1:11:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请问你是哪位\N{\rE}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.49,1:11:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,科尔佐夫\N{\rE}Koltsov.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.58,1:11:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大名呢 要叫我上尉\N{\rE}Your first name? Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.41,1:11:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,科尔佐夫 我是格蕾丝 他是班吉\N{\rE}Koltsov, I'm Grace. That's Benji.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.29,1:11:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能不能花几分钟当回普通人\N{\rE}Could we just, for five minutes, be human beings?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.75,1:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没有俄国人 没有美国人 只有想与心爱的人团聚的普通人\N{\rE}Not Russians, not Americans, just people that want to see our loved ones again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.46,1:12:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有心爱的人 连一条狗都不爱\N{\rE}I have no one. Not even a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.80,1:12:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定没有这把钥匙\N{\rE}Well, you certainly don't have this key.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.05,1:12:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,手上有这把十字形钥匙的人 才能拿到马蹄铁\N{\rE}The cruciform key that grants the holder access to the Podkova.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.72,1:12:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,即使你有坐标\N{\rE}Even if you have the coordinates,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.60,1:12:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没我们帮忙 你也得不到智体的源代码\N{\rE}you still can't safely retrieve the Entity's source code without our help.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.65,1:12:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有一把钥匙\N{\rE}You have another key,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.44,1:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对\N{\rE}don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.24,1:12:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都有钥匙\N{\rE}You've had one all along.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.82,1:12:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你没有的 是坐标\N{\rE}What you don't have are the coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.49,1:12:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等你做出读取器的时候\N{\rE}And when you build the drive,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.12,1:12:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们自然就有了\N{\rE}we will have that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.25,1:12:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧 我们换个思路\N{\rE}Okay, let's try something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.08,1:12:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要是我告诉你 我们有个朋友\N{\rE}What if I told you that we have a friend
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.50,1:12:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他因为拒绝交出钥匙 以至于连政府都不再信任他呢\N{\rE}who's been disavowed by his own government because he refused to hand over this key?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.97,1:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这个朋友正在行动 他不受任何指挥系统的摆布\N{\rE}Our friend is out there right now, independent from any chain of command,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.34,1:12:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就等着我们传送这些坐标\N{\rE}waiting for us to transmit those coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.14,1:12:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他会想尽一切办法\N{\rE}And he will stop at nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.10,1:12:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,安全地取回马蹄铁 并使用存储在里面的源代码\N{\rE}to safely retrieve the Podkova and use the source code stored on it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.68,1:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来铲除智体\N{\rE}to destroy the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.27,1:13:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不是为了某一个国家 为全人类\N{\rE}And not for the sake of any one nation, but for all.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.31,1:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗 智体希望我们相互猜忌\N{\rE}Don't you see? The Entity is counting on us to distrust each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.23,1:13:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了\N{\rE}Please...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.61,1:13:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们完成任务吧\N{\rE}let us complete our mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.86,1:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是你的敌人\N{\rE}We are not enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.53,1:13:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要换做是你 你相信吗\N{\rE}Would you believe that if you were me?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.20,1:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\rE}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.71,1:13:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该也不信\N{\rE}I suppose I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.63,1:13:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,给你们一个小时\N{\rE}You have one hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.17,1:13:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是马克七型压力服\N{\rE}This is the Mark VII pressure suit,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.93,1:13:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它是专门设计出来减少潜入深海后\N{\rE}specifically designed to reduce decompression time
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.39,1:13:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所需的减压时间的\N{\rE}after diving profound depths.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.39,1:13:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它的工作原理 是以特定的比例混合氧气和惰性气体\N{\rE}It does this by means of an exotic mixture of oxygen and inert gases.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.52,1:13:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要长时间做腹式呼吸来适应它\N{\rE}You'll need to do an extended breathe-up for your body to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.27,1:13:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,里面具体混合的是什么气体呢\N{\rE}Exactly what kind of gases are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.57,1:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那就属于机密了\N{\rE}That's classified.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.40,1:13:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,假设你的任务时间在20分钟或以下\N{\rE}Assuming you're on task for twenty minutes or less,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.90,1:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要的减压时间就可以从几天 缩短到几小时\N{\rE}your time in decompression will be cut down from days to hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.70,1:13:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,理论上说是这样 理论上说\N{\rE}Theoretically. Theoretically?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.83,1:14:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,马克七型压力服还没在90米以下测试过\N{\rE}We haven't tested the Mark VII below 300 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.58,1:14:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为了节省氧气 你需要快速进行下潜\N{\rE}To conserve air, you'll need to make a fast descent.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.54,1:14:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就难免会出现HPNS\N{\rE}Which means guaranteed HPNS.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.50,1:14:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,高压神经综合征\N{\rE}High Pressure Nervous Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.34,1:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你会开始发抖\N{\rE}You should expect tremors,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.18,1:14:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,震颤 眩晕\N{\rE}shakes, dizziness,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.93,1:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,会失去方向感 精神混乱\N{\rE}disorientation, and mental confusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.51,1:14:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还要在极高压强下忍受这些\N{\rE}And all of it under extreme pressure.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.43,1:14:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,即便马克七型压力服能够发挥性能\N{\rE}Even if the Mark VII works as designed,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.69,1:14:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你依然没有足够的混合气体来缓慢上浮\N{\rE}you still won't have enough mixture for a slow ascent.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.90,1:14:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也就说 你肯定会得减压病\N{\rE}That means you're guaranteed to get the bends.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.99,1:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你的肌肉组织里的氮元素会溶入血液\N{\rE}Nitrogen in your muscle tissue expands into your bloodstream.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.20,1:14:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,会导致剧烈疼痛\N{\rE}Excruciating pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.53,1:14:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还会抽搐\N{\rE}Convulsions.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.29,1:14:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,完全失去对肌肉的控制\N{\rE}Complete loss of muscle control.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.96,1:14:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你大概有20分钟的时间可以到达减压舱\N{\rE}You'll have maybe twenty minutes to get to the decompression chamber.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.45,1:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 小心 小心头
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.22,1:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要是没有减压舱的话\N{\rE}And without the decompression chamber...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.55,1:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你就死定了\N{\rE}You're a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.18,1:15:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才又做了一轮特高频电波扫描\N{\rE}Another VHF scan came and went.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.14,1:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的朋友们在发送信息\N{\rE}If your friends are broadcasting,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.39,1:15:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们依然没有收到\N{\rE}we still haven't picked it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.99,1:15:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点\N{\rE}Come on, come on, come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.09,1:15:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是谷仓里的雪橇犬在叫 晚餐时间到了\N{\rE}That's the sled dogs out in the barn. It's coming up to dinnertime.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.19,1:15:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告诉你一个小秘密 朋友\N{\rE}I'm gonna let you in on a little secret, friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.15,1:15:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这些磁盘上根本就没有什么坐标\N{\rE}There are no coordinates on any of these disks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.69,1:15:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 14年前所谓的"改装"\N{\rE}That "refit" fourteen years ago?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.49,1:15:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了要掩人耳目\N{\rE}It had all the stench of a cover-up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.20,1:16:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,带队的跟塔蓓萨说话时很傲慢\N{\rE}And the top man talked down to Tapeesa.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.12,1:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常不喜欢\N{\rE}I did not like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.50,1:16:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有把备份的事情告诉他们\N{\rE}I never told them about these backups.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.21,1:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们离开后 我亲自检查了每一个备份\N{\rE}And when they left, I went through every one of them myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.30,1:16:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有一件事非常诡异\N{\rE}A lone event stood out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.01,1:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一次巨大的海底内爆\N{\rE}A massive undersea implosion
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.34,1:16:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,事发时间大约是 他们把资料都拿走的前一个月\N{\rE}about a month before they arrived to take everything away.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.85,1:16:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然不明白其中的意义所在\N{\rE}Naturally, I didn't understand the significance.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.31,1:16:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我把坐标记录了下来 然后\N{\rE}But I noted the coordinates and then
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.48,1:16:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我销毁了那个唯一的磁盘\N{\rE}I destroyed the only disk.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.73,1:16:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说你知道塞瓦斯托波尔号在哪儿\N{\rE}Are you saying you know where the Sevastopol is?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.65,1:16:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,能精确到平方米\N{\rE}Down to the square meter.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.92,1:16:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,该吃晚餐了\N{\rE}Dinnertime.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.21,1:16:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让我妻子去喂一下狗狗吗\N{\rE}Can my wife please tend to the dogs?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.72,1:17:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,狗吠声让我没办法专心做事\N{\rE}I can't concentrate with this racket.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.95,1:17:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]这个上面有坐标\N{\rE}[in Inuktitut]The coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.96,1:17:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]千万多加小心\N{\rE}[in Inuktitut]Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.29,1:17:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]我永远都爱你\N{\rE}[in Inuktitut]I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.96,1:17:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]我们还会再相见的\N{\rE}[in Inuktitut]I will see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.21,1:17:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要搭把手 我去吧\N{\rE}She's gonna need some help. I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.42,1:17:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便透透气\N{\rE}I could use the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.27,1:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[俄语]派个人跟他们一起去\N{\rE}[in Russian]Go with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.37,1:18:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟后开始下一轮信号扫描\N{\rE}Five minutes to the next broadcast window.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.91,1:18:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很快就会到冰盖下面 通讯会中断\N{\rE}We'll be under the ice cap soon and lose all comms.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.29,1:18:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这次是最后一次机会\N{\rE}This will be our last chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.98,1:19:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,值班长 架起一号通讯天线\N{\rE}Chief of the Watch, raise number one comms antenna.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.50,1:19:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 等等 黑格\N{\rE}What? Wait! Wait, Hagar.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.58,1:19:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\rE}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.21,1:19:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 这是什么情况 这是要干什么\N{\rE}Wait. What is this? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.00,1:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你阻止不了智体 伊森\N{\rE}You won't stop the Entity, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.71,1:19:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你得逞\N{\rE}I can't let you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.14,1:20:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,多诺利 快用无线电台 该死\N{\rE}Donloe, get to the radio!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.05,1:20:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把坐标发出去\N{\rE}Send the coordinates!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.90,1:20:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[俄语]跟我打是吧 别做梦了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.42,1:21:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,收到特高频无线电莫尔斯密码\N{\rE}Conn radio! VHF Morse code incoming.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.63,1:21:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,控制室 无线电台
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.76,1:21:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,无线电 赶紧播放\N{\rE}Radio, on speaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.28,1:21:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,黑格\N{\rE}Hagar,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.45,1:21:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你花了太多的\N{\rE}you've spent too much...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.46,1:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,时间\N{\rE}time
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.79,1:21:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在网上了\N{\rE}on the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.06,1:22:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[俄语]他在发坐标\N{\rE}[in Russian]He's sending the coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.64,1:22:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[俄语]我们的人在监听\N{\rE}[in Russian]Our people are listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.19,1:22:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[俄语]屋顶要塌了 快出去\N{\rE}[in Russian]The roof is collapsing. Get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.62,1:23:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.54,1:23:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.23,1:23:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rE}No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.90,1:23:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,多诺利呢\N{\rE}Where's Donloe?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.98,1:23:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,多诺利\N{\rE}Donloe!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.06,1:23:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得走了\N{\rE}We got to go!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.86,1:24:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要的那个坐标\N{\rE}The coordinates you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.49,1:24:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕你上错了潜艇\N{\rE}I'm afraid you're on the wrong boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.11,1:24:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,坐标在好望角 距离约3219公里\N{\rE}That's 2,000 miles off the Cape of Good Hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.37,1:24:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在地球的另一边\N{\rE}On the other side of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.45,1:24:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,位置正好相反\N{\rE}Damn near exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.75,1:24:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"正好"\N{\rE}"Exactly."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.22,1:24:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,正好 相反\N{\rE}Exactly the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.26,1:24:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了防止俄国人监听\N{\rE}In case the Russians were listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.89,1:24:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是巧妙\N{\rE}Very clever.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.31,1:24:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,军官长\N{\rE}Officer of the Deck,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.48,1:24:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,设置新航线 3-4-0\N{\rE}set a new course: 3-4-0.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.52,1:24:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,方向舵右转15度 稳定保持3-4-0航线前进\N{\rE}Right 15 degrees rudder, steady on course 3-4-0.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.48,1:24:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官 方向舵右转15度\N{\rE}Aye, sir. My rudder is right 15.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.19,1:24:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,军官长 发现水下目标 方位1-0-0\N{\rE}Officer of the Deck, submerged contact, bearing 1-0-0.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.86,1:24:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,位于右舷声呐盲区边缘\N{\rE}On the edge of our starboard baffles.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.86,1:25:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,打开扬声器 音调显示是一艘俄罗斯奥斯卡二级潜艇\N{\rE}On speaker. Exhibiting tonals of a Russian Oscar II-class submarine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.49,1:25:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,值班长 火控追踪小组 静默就位\N{\rE}Chief of the Watch, station the fire control tracking party silently.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.41,1:25:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,静默 是 长官 这就完成了一项任务\N{\rE}Silently. Aye, sir. Well, that's one mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.16,1:25:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了别尔哥罗德号\N{\rE}We found the Belgorod.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.83,1:25:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它就跟在我们的后面\N{\rE}It's right on our ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.08,1:25:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你去哪儿执行任务\N{\rE}Wherever your mission is taking you,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.88,1:25:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你都会把俄国人引过去\N{\rE}now you're taking the Russians there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.17,1:25:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他们永远不会知道我的目的地\N{\rE}No, they're never gonna know my destination.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.47,1:25:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们到达坐标地点后 我想让你减速到十节\N{\rE}When we reach those coordinates, I'd like you to slow to ten knots,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.93,1:25:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让潜艇调头\N{\rE}turn this boat around
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.60,1:25:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再把俄国人原路带回去\N{\rE}and take the Russians back the way we came.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.68,1:25:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那你的任务怎么办\N{\rE}What happens to your mission then?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.23,1:25:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在潜艇掉头时下去\N{\rE}I'll be getting off at the turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.98,1:25:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\rE}Mister,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.73,1:25:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要是没有我们的减压舱 你肯定会没命的\N{\rE}without our decompression chamber, you'll die for sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.24,1:25:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 其实你的减压舱原本就不在计划之内\N{\rE}Sir, your decompression chamber was never part of our plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.41,1:25:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\rE}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.16,1:25:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rE}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.33,1:25:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是怎么计划的\N{\rE}What exactly is your plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.13,1:26:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.32,1:26:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rE}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.26,1:26:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.26,1:26:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.10,1:26:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.31,1:26:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,轻拿轻放 减压舱
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.11,1:26:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.02,1:26:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.00,1:26:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\rE}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.95,1:26:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.84,1:26:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗 不 我不会 我不行\N{\rE}Me? No! No, no, I can't. I don't know how. I don't know how.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.54,1:26:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.64,1:26:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\rE}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.89,1:26:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\rE}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.10,1:26:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你示范一下\N{\rE}Yeah. Show me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.72,1:26:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.19,1:26:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这是"左"\N{\rE}That's "left."
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.72,1:26:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.10,1:27:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.64,1:27:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.22,1:27:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.22,1:27:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.31,1:27:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.52,1:27:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.72,1:27:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.70,1:27:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"往前"的意思\N{\rE}"Forward."
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.94,1:27:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.00,1:27:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.57,1:27:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.37,1:27:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是"停下"的意思吗\N{\rE}On this? "Wooh" is stop?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.39,1:27:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.82,1:27:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.05,1:27:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rE}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.74,1:27:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是干什么用的\N{\rE}What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.47,1:27:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.79,1:27:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.00,1:27:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.31,1:27:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,北极熊吗\N{\rE}Polar bear?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.43,1:27:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.43,1:27:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.15,1:28:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.20,1:28:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.62,1:28:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.69,1:28:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的钥匙 还好吗 电源开启\N{\rE}There's your key, okay? Power on.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.23,1:28:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,进行深呼吸\N{\rE}Take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.36,1:28:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,马克七型压力服的导航系统 会带你去坐标点\N{\rE}The Mark VII's guidance system will take you to your coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.11,1:28:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你的位置深度大致是150米\N{\rE}The depth at your location is 500 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.57,1:28:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,前往目标需要19分钟 完成任务需要10分钟\N{\rE}Figure 19 minutes to your target, 10 minutes on task.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.04,1:28:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,记住了\N{\rE}Remember:
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.29,1:28:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果超过预定时间\N{\rE}Any longer than that
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.87,1:28:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你的存活几率每秒都在减少\N{\rE}and your chances of survival decrease by the second.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.96,1:28:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,而且别忘了\N{\rE}And don't forget:
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.63,1:28:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在上浮到水面的过程中 你必须不断呼气\N{\rE}You must exhale continuously as you rise to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.55,1:28:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,屏住呼吸 你的肺就会爆炸\N{\rE}Hold your breath and your lungs will explode.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.59,1:28:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你要的特高频发射器\N{\rE}The VHF transmitter you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.01,1:28:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,半径三公里内 你的队友应该都能找到你\N{\rE}Your team should be able to locate you within a two-mile radius.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.55,1:28:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别弄丢了\N{\rE}Look after that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.89,1:28:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\rE}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.36,1:29:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的压力服别弄坏了\N{\rE}Take care of my suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.76,1:29:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,声纳官 别尔哥罗德号的距离\N{\rE}Sonar, range to Belgorod.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.17,1:29:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 我遇到了近场效应 距离太近看不出\N{\rE}Sir, I have near-field effect. Too close to tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.80,1:29:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,操纵室 按计程仪将速度降到十节\N{\rE}Maneuvering, slow to ten knots by log.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.39,1:29:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,舵手 听我指令 准备右满舵\N{\rE}Helm, on my mark, right full rudder.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.27,1:29:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,随时待命 艇长\N{\rE}Standing by for your mark, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.87,1:30:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,现在转向\N{\rE}Mark the turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.08,1:30:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官 现在右满舵\N{\rE}Aye, sir. My rudder is right full.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.51,1:30:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运 先生\N{\rE}Godspeed, mister.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.61,1:36:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.55,1:41:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼雷发射管\N{\rE}Torpedo tube.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.08,1:48:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了 没事了\N{\rE}It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.89,1:49:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,东西呢\N{\rE}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.35,1:49:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,马蹄铁哪儿去了 怎么不见了 在这里\N{\rE}The Podkova, where is it? Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.48,1:49:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你成功了 伊森\N{\rE}You did it, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.23,1:49:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你成功了\N{\rE}You did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.65,1:49:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那么现在该怎么办\N{\rE}So what happens now?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.24,1:49:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\rE}Now...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.16,1:49:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去找盖布瑞尔\N{\rE}we find Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.83,1:49:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到卢瑟的病毒闪存\N{\rE}We get Luther's poison pill.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.54,1:49:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,然后除掉智体\N{\rE}And we kill the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.09,1:49:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 我一直在想\N{\rE}Ethan, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.09,1:49:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们怎么才能消除智体带来的一切破坏\N{\rE}How can we undo everything the Entity has done?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.80,1:49:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们能控制它\N{\rE}If we could control it,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.64,1:49:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们就能拯救世界于水火之中\N{\rE}maybe we could bring the world back from the brink.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.89,1:49:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rE}Grace...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.40,1:49:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你会希望谁来掌控如此强大的力量呢\N{\rE}who on earth would you ever trust with that much power?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.11,1:49:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是你 毫无疑问\N{\rE}Well, you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.69,1:50:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你\N{\rE}Only you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.36,1:50:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你注定要这么做\N{\rE}I believe you were meant to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.20,1:50:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行\N{\rE}Not me.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.24,1:50:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人都不行\N{\rE}Not anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.29,1:50:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rE}Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.05,1:50:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了我\N{\rE}for bringing me back.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.64,1:50:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这不算什么\N{\rE}Nothing to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.57,1:50:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,说来话长了\N{\rE}It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.06,1:51:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还没正式地做过介绍 我是\N{\rE}We haven't been formally introduced. I'm--
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.77,1:51:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉·多诺利 来自兰利\N{\rE}William Donloe. Langley.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.73,1:51:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们30年前见过\N{\rE}We met thirty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.06,1:51:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\rE}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.82,1:51:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,原来那个就是你\N{\rE}So you're him.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.41,1:51:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我这辈子都欠你的\N{\rE}I understand I owe you my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.24,1:51:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道如何弥补对你造成的影响\N{\rE}I don't know how to make amends for what I've done to yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.12,1:51:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这要看你如何看待它 朋友\N{\rE}That's a matter of perspective, friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.46,1:51:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你30年前没有闯进保险库 我可能还待在那里\N{\rE}If you hadn't broken in the vault 30 years ago, I'd probably still be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.26,1:51:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至可能觉得自己很幸福\N{\rE}I'd probably even think I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.97,1:51:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我就永远无法找到 让我感到宁静的那份归属感\N{\rE}I never would have found the only home that's ever brought me peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.60,1:51:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也绝对不会遇到我的心爱之人\N{\rE}And I certainly never would have met the woman I love.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.19,1:51:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没什么好道歉的\N{\rE}There's nothing to be sorry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.69,1:52:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你改变了我的人生\N{\rE}I owe you my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.75,1:52:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们即将降落 倒计时即将结束\N{\rE}We'll be landing just as the clock runs out.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.88,1:52:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们到达后 智体将掌控\N{\rE}By the time we arrive, the Entity will have control
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.88,1:52:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上九个自动化末日武器库\N{\rE}of the world's nine automated doomsday arsenals.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.50,1:52:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为受控的核导弹注入燃料\N{\rE}And it will be fueling the missiles it controls.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.80,1:52:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它必须潜藏在安全的地方进行发射 否则它也难逃一劫\N{\rE}But it can't launch until it has a safe place to hide if it wants to survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.39,1:52:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,最安全的地方就是这里\N{\rE}The safest place is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.31,1:52:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么 末日保险库 在刚果尤瓦\N{\rE}What is that? The Doomsday Vault. Kongo Yowa.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.48,1:52:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,它是绝密的独立设施 由太阳能供电\N{\rE}It's a top secret standalone, solar-powered,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.02,1:52:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可抵御虚假信号 一级\N{\rE}TEMPEST-hardened, Level A
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.98,1:52:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,艾字节数据服务器\N{\rE}exabyte data server.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.82,1:52:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,储存容量达到十亿千兆字节\N{\rE}One billion gigabytes of storage.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.90,1:52:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,装得下不少电影大片呢 你说的没错\N{\rE}That's a lot of home movies. Well, you're not far off.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.45,1:52:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但凡有保存价值的累积知识 它那儿都有记录\N{\rE}It contains all the accumulated knowledge deemed worthy of preservation.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.74,1:52:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,而且完全屏蔽外界\N{\rE}And it's fully shielded.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.74,1:52:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不受任何电磁能量干扰\N{\rE}Totally impervious to electromagnetic energy of any kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.87,1:52:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,数据无法传入或传出\N{\rE}No transmissions in or out.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.37,1:52:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一只人类史上的不朽方舟\N{\rE}An incorruptible ark of human history
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.54,1:52:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为了在世界末日中幸存而建造\N{\rE}built to survive the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.42,1:53:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 如果智体进入保险库\N{\rE}So, if the Entity got in there,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.67,1:53:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它就可以存活数千年\N{\rE}it could survive for thousands of years,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.05,1:53:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么都不受影响\N{\rE}no matter what happened to the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.76,1:53:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,它想存活是为了什么\N{\rE}And why would it want to survive?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.59,1:53:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,消灭地球上所有生命对它有什么好处\N{\rE}What does it stand to gain from wiping out all life on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.39,1:53:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,诺亚和他的家人肯定在洪水来临之前 问过这个问题\N{\rE}A question Noah and his family must have asked just before the flood.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.52,1:53:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"反上帝"觉得它是上帝\N{\rE}The Anti-God thinks it's God.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.19,1:53:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那要怎么解决\N{\rE}Always
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.69,1:53:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一针见血 你总是这样 对吧\N{\rE}right to the point, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.40,1:53:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是病毒闪存 它写入了卢瑟的算法\N{\rE}This is the poison pill containing Luther's algorithm.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.69,1:53:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个是马蹄铁\N{\rE}And this is the Podkova,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.45,1:53:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,它包含智体的初始源代码\N{\rE}containing the Entity's original source code.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.66,1:53:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把这两者结合 就会生成一种数字化毒素\N{\rE}When combined, they will form a sort of digital toxin.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.41,1:53:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,把它上传到网络空间 毒素就会攻击智体\N{\rE}When uploaded to cyberspace, this toxin will attack the Entity
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.29,1:53:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,并破坏其感知现实的能力\N{\rE}and alter its ability to perceive reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.96,1:53:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是将病毒闪存与马蹄铁结合\N{\rE}So, combine that with the Podkova...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.88,1:53:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就可以欺骗智体这个谎言之神\N{\rE}We can deceive the Lord of Lies.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.18,1:53:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]但是\N{\rE}[in French]But...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.22,1:53:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]总会有个"但是"\N{\rE}[in French]...there's always a but.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.73,1:53:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]但是\N{\rE}[in French]Mais...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.01,1:53:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,卢瑟的病毒闪存不在我们手上\N{\rE}we don't have Luther's poison pill.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.55,1:53:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,被盖布瑞尔抢了\N{\rE}Gabriel does.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.76,1:53:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以能确定 他会在末日保险库等我们过去\N{\rE}Which is why we can be sure he'll be waiting for us in the Doomsday Vault.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.60,1:53:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦智体感染了卢瑟的病毒算法\N{\rE}Once the Entity is infected with Luther's algorithm,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.81,1:54:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它会误认为自己进入了中央数据服务器\N{\rE}it will think it's entering the junction's central data server
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.52,1:54:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但其实 它进入的是这里\N{\rE}when it will actually be going here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.78,1:54:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\rE}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.44,1:54:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,拿稳了 可别摔坏了\N{\rE}Careful, it's very delicate.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.57,1:54:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么可能\N{\rE}It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.32,1:54:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个五维光学数据优盘\N{\rE}It's a 5D optical data drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.12,1:54:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,巴掌大小 但容量可达360太字节\N{\rE}360 terabytes in the palm of your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.58,1:54:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为这个只是理论数值\N{\rE}I thought these were just theoretical.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.58,1:54:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,以前是\N{\rE}They were.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.75,1:54:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,直到卢瑟真的造出来一个\N{\rE}Until Luther built one.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.63,1:54:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,把智体比作要降伏的妖怪\N{\rE}If the Entity is our genie,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.13,1:54:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这个光学优盘就是用来困住它的法器\N{\rE}then this optical drive is the bottle we'll capture it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.18,1:54:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,下面就是棘手的部分\N{\rE}Which brings us to the tricky part.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.10,1:54:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,智体进入之后\N{\rE}Once inside,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.10,1:54:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦它认为自己已经安全\N{\rE}once it believes that it's safe,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.93,1:54:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,它就会立即启动核弹发射程序\N{\rE}the Entity will initiate a nuclear launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.77,1:54:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须在它启动之前 拔出光学优盘\N{\rE}We have to disconnect this drive before it can do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.69,1:54:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有多长时间\N{\rE}How long do we have?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.69,1:54:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,大约\N{\rE}Roughly...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.78,1:54:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,100毫秒\N{\rE}100 milliseconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.36,1:54:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一眨眼的功夫\N{\rE}The blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.28,1:54:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果拔得太快\N{\rE}If we do it too soon...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.28,1:54:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就无法把妖怪困在法器里\N{\rE}We won't trap the genie in the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.12,1:54:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果拔得太慢\N{\rE}Mmm. And if we do it too late...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.04,1:55:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就无法阻止智体发射\N{\rE}We won't prevent the Entity from launching.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.46,1:55:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对 不管怎样\N{\rE}Either way...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.08,1:55:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果拔出优盘的时机不对\N{\rE}If we pull the drive at the wrong time,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.96,1:55:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那智体就赢了\N{\rE}the Entity wins.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.97,1:55:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]祝你好运\N{\rE}[in French]Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.34,1:55:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 如果末日保险库能屏蔽干扰\N{\rE}Hang on. If the Doomsday Vault is electronically shielded,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.63,1:55:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那智体要怎么进去\N{\rE}how does the Entity expect to get in?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.26,1:55:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,智体希望我们让它进去\N{\rE}It expects us to let it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.05,1:55:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就像盖布瑞尔希望我能交出马蹄铁一样\N{\rE}Just like Gabriel expects me to hand over the Podkova.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.31,1:55:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,显然 这两件事我们都不会做\N{\rE}Neither of which we'd ever do, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.77,1:55:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧\N{\rE}Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.39,1:55:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看 保险库能不受电子干扰\N{\rE}Think about it. The vault is electronically shielded.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.81,1:55:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,信号进不去 也出不来\N{\rE}No signals get in or out.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.36,1:55:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就必须有人走出保险库\N{\rE}Someone has to go outside the vault
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.07,1:55:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这样才能将卢瑟的病毒闪存 上传到智体\N{\rE}in order to upload Luther's poison pill to the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.32,1:55:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果盖布瑞尔想控制智体\N{\rE}And if Gabriel wants to control the Entity...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.16,1:55:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他就必须上传卢瑟的病毒闪存才行\N{\rE}He has to upload Luther's poison pill.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.21,1:55:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会要把马蹄铁交给盖布瑞尔\N{\rE}You're not seriously gonna give him the Podkova
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.42,1:55:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,打算让他带着病毒闪存逃脱吧\N{\rE}and let him get away with the pill.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.30,1:55:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这确实就是我打算要做的\N{\rE}That's exactly what I'm going to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.22,1:55:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔会不知不觉地参与咱们的任务\N{\rE}Gabriel will be part of the team and never know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.59,1:55:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,简直是疯了 你居然要让智体进入保险库\N{\rE}That's insane! You're letting the Entity into the vault.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.85,1:56:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做就正如了它的意\N{\rE}That's precisely what it wants you to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.02,1:56:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"一切已成定局"\N{\rE}"It is written."
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.48,1:56:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rE}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.73,1:56:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们打败盖布瑞尔和智体的唯一机会\N{\rE}And it's the only chance we have of beating Gabriel and the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.11,1:56:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,概率小得渺茫的机会\N{\rE}One chance in a trillion.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.52,1:56:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 我劝你再好好想想\N{\rE}Ethan, think about what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.78,1:56:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,想想你是怎么沦落的 想想世界是怎么沦落的\N{\rE}Think about how you got here. Think about how the world got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.45,1:56:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道是不是智体想让你找回马蹄铁\N{\rE}How do you know that the Entity didn't want you to recover the Podkova?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.12,1:56:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也许它告诉你不可能取得回来\N{\rE}Maybe it told you it was impossible
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.83,1:56:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它知道你就是吃这一套\N{\rE}because it knew that was the thing that you needed to hear!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.75,1:56:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是这么想的吗 格蕾丝\N{\rE}Is that what you think, Grace?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.58,1:56:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你正在拿世界的命运冒险\N{\rE}I think you're risking the fate of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.75,1:56:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拿数十亿的生命冒险\N{\rE}and billions of lives
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.17,1:56:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,全在一瞬间\N{\rE}on the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.92,1:56:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 格蕾丝\N{\rE}Yes, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.43,1:56:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,说得对\N{\rE}I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.22,1:56:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果还有别的选择 我愿意接受\N{\rE}And if there was another choice, I'd take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.39,1:56:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们都心存疑虑 我不怪你们\N{\rE}I know you all have your doubts. I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.52,1:56:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们必须团结一心\N{\rE}But we have to stick together.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.65,1:56:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得确保让格蕾丝\N{\rE}And we have to make sure that Grace
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.23,1:56:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,负责拔出光学优盘\N{\rE}is the one to disconnect that drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.15,1:56:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,让我\N{\rE}Me?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.07,1:56:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,让神偷和小偷拉开差距的关键是什么\N{\rE}What separates a good pickpocket from a great one?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.37,1:57:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,时机\N{\rE}Timing.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.46,1:57:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,全在一瞬间\N{\rE}Blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.15,1:57:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,刚果尤瓦\N{\rE}南非
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.70,1:57:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,人都上哪儿去了\N{\rE}Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.66,1:57:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大家知道要出大事\N{\rE}They know what's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.62,1:57:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以全躲在家里\N{\rE}They've all gone home.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.32,1:58:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,离线
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.75,1:58:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,0天0小时27分钟
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.25,1:58:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,俄罗斯
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.27,1:58:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,当前智体的行动速度 超出了我们的预测范围\N{\rE}We can't accurately predict how fast the Entity is moving now.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.36,1:58:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 亨特已经不在了\N{\rE}Madam President, Hunt is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.99,1:59:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就算他没死 也被俄国人抓走了\N{\rE}If he isn't dead, the Russians have him.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.45,1:59:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们失去了对武器库的控制\N{\rE}If we lose control of our arsenal,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.57,1:59:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就失去了阻止智体发射核武器的希望\N{\rE}we lose any hope of preventing the Entity from launching.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.20,1:59:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没时间了\N{\rE}We are out of time!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.00,1:59:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,西德尼将军\N{\rE}General Sidney...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.54,1:59:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最低限度的攻击方案是什么\N{\rE}what is our most limited attack option?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.25,1:59:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小范围内进行精确打击\N{\rE}Surgical nuclear strikes
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.09,1:59:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把打击范围严格限制在由智体控制的\N{\rE}confined strictly to the command centers of the eight nations
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.26,1:59:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,八国核指挥中心\N{\rE}under the Entity's control.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.97,1:59:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,北京 伊斯兰堡 伦敦\N{\rE}Beijing. Islamabad. London.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.72,1:59:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,莫斯科 新德里 巴黎\N{\rE}Moscow. New Delhi. Paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.14,1:59:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,平壤 和特拉维夫\N{\rE}Pyongyang. And Tel Aviv.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:33.85,1:59:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,伤亡情况\N{\rE}Casualties.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.73,1:59:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,初次袭击造成的死亡人数预估\N{\rE}Estimated death tolls from initial strikes.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:40.36,1:59:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还有后续更多伤亡 来自核放射尘埃\N{\rE}And more later, of course, from the resulting nuclear fallout.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.62,1:59:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,估计 情况不一\N{\rE}Estimates, uh... vary.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.91,1:59:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,显然 对八个不同国家的主要城市进行轰炸\N{\rE}Obviously the bombing of major cities in eight different countries
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.08,1:59:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,会造成前所未有的政治危机\N{\rE}would create an unprecedented political crisis.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.00,2:00:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很可能酿成一场持久的全球战争\N{\rE}One that would likely lead to a protracted global war.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.46,2:00:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也许外交上谨慎的做法是展现\N{\rE}It may be diplomatically prudent to make a...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.09,2:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,姿态\N{\rE}gesture.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.14,2:00:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,展现姿态\N{\rE}A gesture?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.02,2:00:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们国家也牺牲一座城市\N{\rE}Sacrifice one of our cities here at home.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.27,2:00:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备了清单\N{\rE}We've prepared a list.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.44,2:00:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,各座城市 是根据战略和经济重要性来整理的\N{\rE}Cities have been arranged by strategic and economic importance.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.86,2:00:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rE}And...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.24,2:00:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也要考虑人口因素\N{\rE}...population, of course.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.82,2:00:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你想拿一亿人的性命\N{\rE}You'd be sacrificing a hundred million lives...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.25,2:00:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,去换七十亿人的命\N{\rE}to save seven billion.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.00,2:00:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能发生这种事\N{\rE}This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.92,2:00:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士\N{\rE}Madam President,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.25,2:00:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在身处智体构造的现实中\N{\rE}we are in the Entity's reality now.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.17,2:00:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而且完全没有胜算\N{\rE}And this is checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.28,2:01:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,枪炮军士 我需要你的手枪\N{\rE}Gunnery Sergeant, I need your sidearm.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.28,2:01:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\rE}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.74,2:01:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令 孩子 赶快给我\N{\rE}You heard me, son. Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.46,2:01:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,主服务器在那边\N{\rE}The main server's through there.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.72,2:01:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,班吉 格蕾丝 你们跟我来\N{\rE}Now, Benji, Grace, you come with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.05,2:01:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人在这里等着\N{\rE}The rest of you, you just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.93,2:01:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rE}Non.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.19,2:01:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]盖布瑞尔就在里面\N{\rE}[in French]Gabriel is down there.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.16,2:01:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]我跟你一起去\N{\rE}[in French]Let me come with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.57,2:01:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]他迟早要完蛋的\N{\rE}[in French]His time will come.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.43,2:01:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]好吧
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.96,2:02:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那是通往服务器的门\N{\rE}That's the door to the server room.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:06.21,2:02:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,它的位置太明显了\N{\rE}It's too exposed.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.22,2:02:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们应该去跟其他人汇合\N{\rE}You should go back to the others.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.30,2:02:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果盖布瑞尔在里面 他会杀了你的\N{\rE}If Gabriel is in there, he'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.39,2:02:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他必须确保带着病毒闪存和马蹄铁离开\N{\rE}He has to leave here with the pill and the Podkova.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.48,2:02:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以牺牲 但你们不可以\N{\rE}I'm expendable. Neither of you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.40,2:02:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他说得对\N{\rE}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.28,2:02:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,照顾好你的团队\N{\rE}Take care of your team.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.46,2:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你的最终清算\N{\rE}Your final reckoning!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:43.81,2:03:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,三千万吨炸药\N{\rE}Thirty megaton yield.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.81,2:03:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人只要按一下按钮 智体就无所遁形了\N{\rE}My man lets go of that button and the Entity has no place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:50.15,2:03:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那你又该怎么办\N{\rE}And what happens to you?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.15,2:03:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我有飞机 可以撤离到最近安全距离\N{\rE}I have a plane that'll take me to minimum safe distance.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.07,2:03:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很稳妥 有模拟信号 雷达探测不到\N{\rE}Reliable, analog, under the radar.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.99,2:04:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我还安排了备用飞机 确保万无一失\N{\rE}I even brought a spare. Just in case.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.25,2:04:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的相信摧毁这个地方\N{\rE}And you honestly believe destroying this place
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.79,2:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,能阻止智体发射核弹吗\N{\rE}will stop the Entity from launching.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.46,2:04:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这是幌子\N{\rE}I think it's bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.09,2:04:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不让它进入 它就不能存在\N{\rE}It won't end the world if it can't survive,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.01,2:04:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,它不能存在 就无法毁灭世界\N{\rE}and it can't survive if you don't let it in.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.22,2:04:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快把马蹄铁交出来\N{\rE}Now hand over the Podkova
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.34,2:04:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你离开\N{\rE}and I'll let you walk away.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.97,2:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我凭什么相信你 因为我希望你\N{\rE}Why would I believe that? Because I want you
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.26,2:04:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还有每个你在意的人\N{\rE}and everyone you care about
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.77,2:04:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都能在我创造的世界里长命百岁\N{\rE}to live long lives in the world I create
Dialogue: 0,2:04:26.06,2:04:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只要等智体听命于我\N{\rE}when the Entity answers to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:28.56,2:04:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经败了 伊森\N{\rE}You're beat, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.23,2:04:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,即便不是今天 也会是其他时间 其他的地点\N{\rE}If not today, some other place, some other time.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.07,2:04:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我掌握了这个\N{\rE}As long as I have this,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.37,2:04:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,无论我去哪里 你都会跟随\N{\rE}wherever I go, you will follow.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.53,2:04:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,马蹄铁自然会送上门来\N{\rE}And the Podkova will come to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.25,2:04:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一切已成定局\N{\rE}That is written.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:45.21,2:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没有什么定局\N{\rE}Nothing is written.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.46,2:04:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,卢瑟或许不会这么想吧\N{\rE}I'm not sure Luther would agree.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.46,2:04:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\rE}Now,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.88,2:04:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快点说 我赢了\N{\rE}tell me I win!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.52,2:05:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你赢了\N{\rE}You win.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:07.65,2:05:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这句话真好听\N{\rE}I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.31,2:05:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一遍\N{\rE}Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.98,2:05:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\rE}Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.07,2:05:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\rE}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.57,2:05:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把双手举起来 混蛋\N{\rE}Hands where I can see them, dickhead.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.00,2:05:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.44,2:05:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吧\N{\rE}Let's have it.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.11,2:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要多久\N{\rE}Time?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.31,2:05:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,18分钟\N{\rE}18 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.53,2:05:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识你\N{\rE}I know you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.70,2:06:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,多诺利\N{\rE}Donloe.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.16,2:06:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉·多诺利\N{\rE}William Donloe.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.62,2:06:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的妻子 塔蓓萨\N{\rE}My wife, Tapeesa.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.91,2:06:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我真佩服你 亨特 你组建的这一支小队配置简直无敌了\N{\rE}I got to hand it to you, Hunt. This is one crackerjack unit you've put together.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.79,2:06:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在想象智体穿着虚拟短裤 吓得瑟瑟发抖的样子了\N{\rE}I'm imagining the Entity is shaking in its virtual shorts right about now.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.13,2:06:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西有什么用 你们的计划到底是什么\N{\rE}What do I need to know about this, and what exactly was the play?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:17.17,2:06:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,计划就是把东西给他 然后放他走 立刻马上\N{\rE}The only play is to give that to him, and let him go right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:20.47,2:06:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把这个东西给他 再放他走\N{\rE}You want me to give this to him and let him go.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.14,2:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻马上 立刻马上\N{\rE}Right now. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:24.68,2:06:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻马上 立刻马上\N{\rE}Right now. Right now...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:26.89,2:06:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,美国总统正准备\N{\rE}the President of the United States
Dialogue: 0,2:06:28.89,2:06:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让数百万人的生命瞬间化作一缕青烟\N{\rE}is preparing to vaporize millions upon millions of souls.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:31.73,2:06:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是因为伊森觉得 任何人都没办法安全地控制智体\N{\rE}All because Ethan here doesn't believe that anyone can safely control the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.32,2:06:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来很有道理吗\N{\rE}Does that sound sane? To anyone?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:40.24,2:06:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你该问问塞瓦斯托波尔号的官兵\N{\rE}Maybe you should ask the crew of the Sevastopol.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:45.66,2:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,时间 17分钟 长官\N{\rE}Time? 17 minutes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.66,2:06:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,基特里奇 伊森没有计划 你们就不会在这儿了\N{\rE}Kittridge. You wouldn't be here if Ethan didn't have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:50.83,2:06:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谁把计划告诉我\N{\rE}Whomever tells me what that plan is
Dialogue: 0,2:06:53.38,2:06:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,谁就可以拯救几百万人的生命 而且还可以免受惩罚\N{\rE}will be sparing millions of lives, and you'll be spared the fate of the others.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:57.25,2:06:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没时间了 我们需要撤到安全地带\N{\rE}Sir, we're running out of time. We need to get to a minimum safe distance.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:59.72,2:07:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还要在这里\N{\rE}Why are we still standing here?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.09,2:07:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他在这里 他也在这里\N{\rE}Because he's here and he's here.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:04.01,2:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西肯定有什么作用\N{\rE}And this means something.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:07.10,2:07:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,用不了多久\N{\rE}Any second now
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.72,2:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森就会把一切都告诉我\N{\rE}Ethan's gonna tell me what it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.64,2:07:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我和这个人认识很久了\N{\rE}I've known this man for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.36,2:07:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他绝对不允许他的宝贝队友出现任何闪失\N{\rE}And he won't want anything to happen to his precious team.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.07,2:07:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的行事原则 对吧\N{\rE}And that's the pattern, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.74,2:07:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝不允许\N{\rE}You refuse to sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,2:07:29.87,2:07:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你所珍爱之人出现任何牺牲\N{\rE}the ones you hold close.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.63,2:07:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们会在这里\N{\rE}That is why we're still here.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.96,2:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了\N{\rE}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:39.46,2:07:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么丢脸的\N{\rE}There's no shame in it.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.63,2:07:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那么现在\N{\rE}Now just...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.76,2:07:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,把知道的都告诉我\N{\rE}tell me what I'm missing.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:45.72,2:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,时间\N{\rE}Time.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:02.11,2:08:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 行动\N{\rE}Okay. Now!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.09,2:08:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,盖布瑞尔\N{\rE}Gabriel!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.43,2:08:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,帕丽斯 盖布瑞尔 马上杀了他\N{\rE}Paris, Gabriel now! Kill him now!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.64,2:08:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,德加 打盖布瑞尔 开枪打死他 打死他\N{\rE}Degas! Gabriel! Shoot him, shoot him, kill him! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.15,2:08:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有本事就来抓我呀 伊森\N{\rE}Catch me if you can, Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:39.19,2:08:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你去追他 把闪存夺回来\N{\rE}You go after him and get the pill.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.07,2:08:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去服务器室 让智体进去\N{\rE}We'll get to the server room and let the Entity in.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:46.95,2:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 我们会想出办法的\N{\rE}Ethan, we'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.78,2:08:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了有炸弹 那可是核弹\N{\rE}You are forgetting the bomb. The nuclear bomb.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.54,2:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会想出办法的\N{\rE}We'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:53.37,2:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 班吉\N{\rE}Ethan! Benji.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.58,2:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 这儿交给我\N{\rE}Go! I got this.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:56.17,2:08:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\rE}Go.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:00.96,2:09:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,全在一瞬间\N{\rE}Blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.30,2:09:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,帕丽斯 掩护\N{\rE}Paris! Cover, cover!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:13.14,2:09:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,亨特\N{\rE}Hunt!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.01,2:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,2:09:17.56,2:09:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为他不愿意走\N{\rE}I thought he'd never leave.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.57,2:09:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,会想出办法的\N{\rE}We'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.49,2:09:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得走了 布里格斯\N{\rE}We got to go, Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.79,2:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你就没命了 赶紧走\N{\rE}It's your funeral. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.97,2:11:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一定有办法能解除它\N{\rE}There has to be a way to disarm it.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.81,2:12:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是你能阻止它触发核爆炸\N{\rE}Even if you can prevent it from going nuclear,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:01.48,2:12:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有办法阻止引爆器的爆炸\N{\rE}you can't stop those detonators from exploding.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:03.73,2:12:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,服务器房间能经受住爆炸吗\N{\rE}Could we survive the blast from the server room?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:05.69,2:12:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,除非有人留在外面 阻止核弹达到临界质量\N{\rE}Only if someone stays behind and stops the bomb from going critical.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.82,2:12:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但不管是谁 都会没命的\N{\rE}But whoever that is, they're not going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:13.96,2:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]谁能活着 谁又要赴死呢\N{\rE}[in French]Who will live and who will die?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:19.62,2:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来处理炸弹 其他人带班吉去服务器室\N{\rE}We'll handle the bomb. The rest of you get Benji to the server room.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.54,2:12:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间商量了 快去\N{\rE}There's no time to discuss it. Go.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.60,2:12:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[因纽特语]我们还会再相见的\N{\rE}[in Inuktitut]I will see you again.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:31.34,2:12:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,用力按住\N{\rE}Keep pressure on it.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:32.76,2:12:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我按住了 按住了\N{\rE}I've got it. I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:36.59,2:12:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他们一起\N{\rE}I'll stay with them.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.18,2:12:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,反正服务器室我也帮不上忙\N{\rE}There's nothing for me to do in the server room.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:41.77,2:12:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你们好运\N{\rE}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.43,2:12:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你们好运\N{\rE}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.82,2:14:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你是从哪学来的\N{\rE}Where'd you learn to do this?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:16.23,2:14:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我又没说我学过\N{\rE}Never said I did.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:36.84,2:14:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 感觉不太对 怎么了\N{\rE}This is not good. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.22,2:14:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没猜错的话 这是张力性气胸\N{\rE}If I had to guess, it's a tension pneumothorax.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:41.72,2:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思 胸腔内的压力在增大\N{\rE}What does that mean? Pressure building in the pleural cavity.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:45.31,2:14:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的肺要萎缩了\N{\rE}My lung is collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.14,2:14:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不赶紧行动 我就会窒息或者心脏骤停\N{\rE}If we don't act fast, it means suffocation or cardiac arrest.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:50.94,2:14:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有谁学过医的吗\N{\rE}Do either of you have any medical experience?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:55.00,2:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]我只懂杀人\N{\rE}[in French]I kill people.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:57.07,2:14:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就你了\N{\rE}I can work with that.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:58.53,2:15:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 我需要你黑进服务器\N{\rE}Grace, I need you to hack the server
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.36,2:15:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好让智体进来\N{\rE}so we can let the Entity in.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.16,2:15:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,拿上工具 去找控制面板 帕丽斯\N{\rE}Grab the tools, head to the panel. Paris.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:04.76,2:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]你必须给我动手术\N{\rE}[in French]You have to operate on me.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:06.03,2:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]我吗\N{\rE}[in French]Moi?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:07.02,2:15:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]你听我说
Dialogue: 0,2:15:08.16,2:15:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 我要你把弹孔堵住 保证气密性\N{\rE}First I need you to plug the bullet hole, make it airtight.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.01,2:15:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]要密封起来\N{\rE}[in French]Close it tight.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.22,2:15:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]再用绷带\N{\rE}[in French]A bandage.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.43,2:15:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]快给我拿绷带\N{\rE}[in French]A bandage please.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:10.56,2:16:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我进来了 然后干吗\N{\rE}I'm in. What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:12.64,2:16:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 找一找电源开关\N{\rE}Grace, I need you to find the power switch...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:14.56,2:16:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,服务器内网的开关\N{\rE}...to the server's internal network.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:16.15,2:16:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 帕丽斯\N{\rE}Got it. Paris.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:17.79,2:16:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]从锁骨 数到第二根肋骨的位置\N{\rE}[in French]My clavicle... count down to my second rib.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:22.71,2:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]现在\N{\rE}[in French]Now...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:24.42,2:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]切开一个口子\N{\rE}[in French]...make an incision.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:33.43,2:16:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]拿着\N{\rE}[in French]Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.42,2:16:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,帕丽斯\N{\rE}Paris.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:38.43,2:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]不会有事的\N{\rE}[in French]It's going to be OK.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:41.10,2:16:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]把它喝完\N{\rE}[in French]Bottoms up.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:49.36,2:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]然后呢\N{\rE}[in French]Now what?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:50.40,2:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]笔 在袋子里\N{\rE}[in French]Pen... in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:51.49,2:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]压住\N{\rE}[in French]Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:53.07,2:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]得把它拆开\N{\rE}[in French]Take it apart.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:54.43,2:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 你找到开关了吗\N{\rE}Grace, did you find the switch?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:56.44,2:16:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 好 把它关掉\N{\rE}Yeah. Okay, shut it off.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:58.48,2:17:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢 打开控制面板\N{\rE}What next? Open the panel.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:01.24,2:17:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]接着呢\N{\rE}[in French]Now what?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:02.24,2:17:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,把它插进切口\N{\rE}Push that into the incision.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:04.69,2:17:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rE}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:16.22,2:17:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]谢谢你\N{\rE}[in French]Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:20.21,2:17:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N{\rE}Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:21.88,2:17:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,德加 你那儿情况怎么样\N{\rE}Degas, how's it going in there?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:23.80,2:17:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,全都在可控范围内\N{\rE}Uh, everything's under control here.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:26.13,2:17:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 一定要把它拿稳了\N{\rE}Okay, hold this very steady.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:29.18,2:17:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是千万别拔出来\N{\rE}But don't pull it out.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.04,2:17:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我说的 伊森\N{\rE}It's like I said, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:58.50,2:18:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,只要病毒闪存在我手上\N{\rE}As long as I have the pill...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:01.46,2:18:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,马蹄铁就会自己找上门来\N{\rE}the Podkova will come to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.05,2:18:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 什么 怎么回事\N{\rE}Hang on. What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:56.14,2:18:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有办法能逃脱\N{\rE}We may have a way out of this.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:58.48,2:19:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的地线有三倍冗余\N{\rE}These ground wires are triple redundant.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:01.27,2:19:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果同时切断任意三根地线的话\N{\rE}If we cut any three of them simultaneously,
Dialogue: 0,2:19:03.65,2:19:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以推迟引爆器的爆炸时间\N{\rE}we could delay these detonators from exploding.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:06.32,2:19:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也许能为跑到服务器室争取时间\N{\rE}Maybe long enough for someone to make it to the server room.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:08.74,2:19:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,多长时间\N{\rE}How long?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.15,2:19:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,十秒钟 差不多\N{\rE}Ten seconds. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:14.24,2:19:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得在十秒钟内能跑到那扇门吗\N{\rE}You think you can make it to that door in ten seconds?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:19.58,2:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只有试过才知道 套筒扳手给我\N{\rE}Only one way to find out. Hand me the ratchet.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:22.08,2:19:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 打开了 然后呢 危险还没解除\N{\rE}Okay, I'm in. What now? We're not out of the woods yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:25.46,2:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我的血压随时可能急剧下降\N{\rE}Any minute now, my blood pressure's gonna drop drastically
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.59,2:19:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我随时有可能晕倒 所以我们必须要速战速决\N{\rE}and I'll grow faint, so we need to work fast.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:30.76,2:19:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,工具袋里有个接收器 一个银色盒子 上面有两盏灯\N{\rE}There's a receiver in the tool bag. A silver box with two lights on it.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:34.26,2:19:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了\N{\rE}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:35.97,2:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,把它接到服务器的太阳能电池板上\N{\rE}We need to splice that into the server's solar panels
Dialogue: 0,2:19:37.35,2:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用它当天线\N{\rE}and make an antenna.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:38.43,2:19:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,来判断伊森什么时候上传病毒闪存\N{\rE}That way we'll know when Ethan's uploading the poison pill.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:41.43,2:19:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好 明白 好 接下来就要上难度了\N{\rE}Yep. Got it. Now this is the really tricky part.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:43.60,2:19:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有一束蓝黑红色的线缆\N{\rE}There is a bundle of blue, black, and red cables
Dialogue: 0,2:19:46.15,2:19:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在右下角的位置\N{\rE}in the lower right corner.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:48.07,2:19:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好 跟我详细说说\N{\rE}All right. Walk me through it.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:50.03,2:19:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你按照特定的顺序 剪断两根电线\N{\rE}I'm gonna need you to cut two of the wires in a specific order,
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.86,2:19:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是无论怎么样 都别剪断\N{\rE}but whatever you do, do not cut...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:59.37,2:20:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,班吉 红色那根\N{\rE}Benji! ...the red ones.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:01.96,2:20:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一\N{\rE}级\N{\rE}防\N{\rE}御\N{\rE}状\N{\rE}态
Dialogue: 0,2:20:03.29,2:20:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 我作为美国的国防部长\N{\rE}Madam President, as your Secretary of Defense
Dialogue: 0,2:20:06.46,2:20:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在此向您提出申请\N{\rE}I direct your attention to CONPLAN 8044,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:10.34,2:20:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看一看"8044概念规划"\N{\rE}selected Attack Option 9.1.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:13.09,2:20:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,里面选定的第9.1条攻击方案 针对目前由智体控制的\N{\rE}A targeted nuclear strike on the command centers
Dialogue: 0,2:20:15.84,2:20:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,所有八国核指挥中心进行针对性核打击\N{\rE}of all eight nations now controlled by the Entity.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:19.14,2:20:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这其中也包括了 您选择牺牲的一座美国城市\N{\rE}Amended to include the American city you've chosen to sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:25.10,2:20:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,密码卡\N{\rE}The Biscuit.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:39.41,2:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,跟您的儿子聊过了吗\N{\rE}Have you spoken to your son?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:43.25,2:20:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他聊什么呢\N{\rE}What would I tell him?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.33,2:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,验证码已通过\N{\rE}Authentication code verified.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.84,2:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\rE}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:04.64,2:21:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 伊森\N{\rE}Come on, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:06.27,2:21:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你很清楚你输定了\N{\rE}Know when you're beat.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.77,2:21:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的团队随时都可能丧命\N{\rE}Any minute now your team will be dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:10.36,2:21:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,而且智体也将永无藏身之地\N{\rE}And the Entity will have no place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:27.58,2:21:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你耍到筋疲力尽\N{\rE}I'm gonna run you into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:29.75,2:21:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,马蹄铁一定是我的\N{\rE}The Podkova will be mine
Dialogue: 0,2:21:32.38,2:21:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,将来智体也会听我号令\N{\rE}and the Entity will answer to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.22,2:21:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是迟早的事\N{\rE}It's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:39.14,2:21:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 我们可以阻止炸弹触发核爆\N{\rE}Ow. Grace, we think we can prevent this bomb from going nuclear,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:42.10,2:21:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但所有的引爆器同样会爆炸\N{\rE}but all of these detonators will explode.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:43.43,2:21:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有多大威力\N{\rE}How big a blast?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:45.43,2:21:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸威力有多大\N{\rE}How big a blast are we talking?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:48.73,2:21:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很大\N{\rE}Big.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:50.36,2:21:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要尽量给伊森争取时间\N{\rE}Ethan needs all the time we can give him.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:52.23,2:21:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不到最后关头 千万别把线剪断\N{\rE}Do not make the last cut until we absolutely have to.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:00.78,2:22:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士\N{\rE}Madam President,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:02.49,2:22:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,发射面板已开启\N{\rE}launch is now enabled.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:33.36,2:22:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了\N{\rE}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:34.98,2:22:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一开始就应该这样做了\N{\rE}What we should have done in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:38.11,2:22:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,去通知美国战略指挥中心 把电源切断\N{\rE}Order U.S. Strategic Command Center to cut their power.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:42.82,2:22:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,完全关闭我们的核导弹\N{\rE}Take our missiles offline entirely.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:46.16,2:22:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,能关的全部关闭\N{\rE}Shut everything down.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:48.16,2:22:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 那样整个国家就会暴露在他人的攻击下\N{\rE}Madam President, that would leave the country completely defenseless.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:51.62,2:22:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样也能阻止智体 进入地球上最大的核武器库\N{\rE}But deny the Entity access to the largest nuclear arsenal on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:56.25,2:22:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧 打电话\N{\rE}Now, make the call.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:57.71,2:22:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N{\rE}Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:59.13,2:23:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 我们可是地球上\N{\rE}Ma'am, We are the only nation on Earth
Dialogue: 0,2:23:00.84,2:23:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一有能力攻击智体的国家\N{\rE}with the power to attack the Entity!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:02.93,2:23:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也是世界上唯一拥有选择权的国家\N{\rE}And now we're the only nation in the world with the power of choice.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:05.64,2:23:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我选择不发动进攻\N{\rE}Today I choose not to attack.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:07.89,2:23:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 请你再考虑一下\N{\rE}Madam President, think this through.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.64,2:23:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,您这么做是大错特错\N{\rE}You are making a terrible mistake!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:11.64,2:23:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为了国家 请听取理性的建议\N{\rE}For the sake of the country, please listen to reason.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:13.98,2:23:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,正是如此\N{\rE}That's precisely what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:15.40,2:23:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我接通战略司令部总部 好的\N{\rE}Connect me with Strategic Command HQ.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:17.78,2:23:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不按下那个按钮 数百万人就会丧命\N{\rE}Millions of people will die, ma'am, if you don't push that button.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:20.24,2:23:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她按了 也有数百万人丧命\N{\rE}And millions of other people will die if she does!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:22.16,2:23:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谁给我们的权力来决定他人的生死\N{\rE}What give us the right to decide who lives and who dies?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:24.07,2:23:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她就任总统的时候宣过誓\N{\rE}She took an oath as President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:26.24,2:23:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,发射出去20分钟后 这些都不重要了 什么都不重要了\N{\rE}Twenty minutes after we launch, none of that will matter!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:28.91,2:23:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我倾向于总统这边\N{\rE}I'm inclined to agree with the President.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:31.04,2:23:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们站在这里争论的时候 智体正在准备发动进攻\N{\rE}While we stand here arguing, the Entity is preparing to attack, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:34.04,2:23:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以选择活在智体构造的现实中 先生们 但我不行\N{\rE}You may choose to live in the Entity's reality, gentlemen. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:38.13,2:23:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是总统找您\N{\rE}Hold for the President.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:39.67,2:23:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,战略司令部 奥弗顿将军的办公室\N{\rE}General Overton's office, Strategic Command.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:41.80,2:23:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,奥弗顿将军 我是总统 我找你是要下达一项非常规命令\N{\rE}General Overton, this is the President calling with an unorthodox command.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:45.85,2:23:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请你认真地听我的指示\N{\rE}I need you to listen to my instructions very carefully
Dialogue: 0,2:23:48.56,2:23:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,并且严格执行命令不得有丝毫闪失\N{\rE}and follow them to the letter without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:58.36,2:24:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士 埃丽卡 我没事 我没事\N{\rE}Madam President? I'm fine. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:15.75,2:24:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,将军\N{\rE}General!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:19.42,2:24:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,总统女士\N{\rE}Madam President.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:33.33,2:24:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,离线
Dialogue: 0,2:24:38.18,2:24:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,美国
Dialogue: 0,2:24:49.69,2:24:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,美国
Dialogue: 0,2:25:07.18,2:25:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,智体已经在给导弹注入燃料了\N{\rE}The Entity will be fueling its missiles by now,
Dialogue: 0,2:25:09.43,2:25:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,趁导弹没发射 它要找地方藏起来\N{\rE}but it still needs a place to hide before it launches.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:11.81,2:25:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了 格蕾丝 搞定了 弄完了\N{\rE}Talk to me, Grace. I've got it. It's done.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:14.43,2:25:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,接收器已经连上了\N{\rE}Receiver's connected.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:15.77,2:25:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 开始吧\N{\rE}Okay. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:17.15,2:25:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们要重新启动电源\N{\rE}We're gonna switch the power back on.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:21.77,2:25:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,已启动接收器 红灯亮了\N{\rE}Receiver's activated. Red light is on.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:23.44,2:25:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,德加 你那儿怎么样\N{\rE}Degas, how we doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:24.94,2:25:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 正在取出最后一个引爆器\N{\rE}Great. We're extracting the last detonator.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:26.49,2:25:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好切断引线了\N{\rE}We're ready to cut the fuses.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:27.61,2:25:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还有四分钟\N{\rE}Four minutes on the clock.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:29.20,2:25:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,明白 四分钟\N{\rE}Understood. Four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:30.87,2:25:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,把优盘插进去\N{\rE}Insert the drive.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.66,2:25:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,准备就绪\N{\rE}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:34.50,2:25:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你盯着接收器上的指示灯\N{\rE}Now, you're gonna watch the lights on the receiver.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:36.83,2:25:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等红灯变\N{\rE}When the red light turns--
Dialogue: 0,2:25:39.88,2:25:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 抱歉\N{\rE}What? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:41.88,2:25:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看到红灯变绿\N{\rE}When the red light turns green,
Dialogue: 0,2:25:43.88,2:25:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就说明 伊森已经把病毒闪存连接到了马蹄铁\N{\rE}you'll know Ethan has connected the pill to the Podkova
Dialogue: 0,2:25:47.09,2:25:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,并且智体已经被卢瑟的算法感染了\N{\rE}and the Entity has been infected with Luther's algorithm.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:49.64,2:25:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 再然后呢\N{\rE}Okay. Then what?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:51.47,2:25:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 把那根红线剪断 把智体放进来\N{\rE}Then you're gonna cut that red wire and let the Entity in.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:55.81,2:25:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只需要等伊森拿到病毒闪存\N{\rE}All we need now is for Ethan to get that pill.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:59.65,2:26:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定有办法\N{\rE}He'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.82,2:27:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rE}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:13.91,2:29:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊 这就对了嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:29:17.58,2:29:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森
Dialogue: 0,2:29:35.85,2:29:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,启动装置
Dialogue: 0,2:30:30.00,2:30:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜只有我戴了降落伞\N{\rE}Only one of us has a parachute!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:33.09,2:30:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,自求多福吧\N{\rE}Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:20.30,2:31:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快没有时间了\N{\rE}We're almost out of time.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:22.05,2:31:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再过十秒我就要从三开始倒数\N{\rE}At 10 seconds I'm gonna count backwards from three.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:24.85,2:31:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,三 二 一 切断\N{\rE}Three, two, one, cut.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:27.35,2:31:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然后咱们拼命往门那边跑\N{\rE}Then we run like hell for that door.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:29.27,2:31:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,记住 等光学优盘亮起\N{\rE}Remember, when that drive lights up
Dialogue: 0,2:31:31.48,2:31:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就说明智体已经进入了\N{\rE}you'll know the Entity's inside.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:33.31,2:31:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你有100毫秒的时间\N{\rE}You have 100 milliseconds.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:36.46,2:31:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[法语]全在一瞬间\N{\rE}[in French]The blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:40.05,2:32:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里 伊森\N{\rE}Where are you, Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:04.78,2:33:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森\N{\rE}Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:39.46,2:34:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我是总统\N{\rE}This is the President.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:52.05,2:34:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他成功了\N{\rE}He did it.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:56.64,2:34:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那个混蛋还真的做到了\N{\rE}That son of a bitch actually did it.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:25.63,2:35:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 兄弟\N{\rE}Hello, brother.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:29.88,2:35:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,当你听到这段录音\N{\rE}If you're listening to this,
Dialogue: 0,2:35:32.34,2:35:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就说明世界依然存在\N{\rE}the world is still here.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:34.55,2:35:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你也还活着\N{\rE}And so are you.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:37.10,2:35:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 我就知道你一定会成功\N{\rE}For the record, I never had a moment of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:42.77,2:35:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你一定会想到办法\N{\rE}I knew you'd find a way.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:47.15,2:35:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是有办法\N{\rE}You always do.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:51.57,2:35:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望有一天 你能明白这样的人生\N{\rE}I hope in time you can see this life
Dialogue: 0,2:35:55.07,2:35:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是什么天意弄人\N{\rE}was not some quirk of fate.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:58.29,2:36:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你的使命\N{\rE}This was your calling.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:01.46,2:36:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的宿命\N{\rE}Your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:03.50,2:36:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你的宿命关系到这个世界所有生物\N{\rE}A destiny that touches every living thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:09.96,2:36:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不管愿不愿意 我们都是自己命运的主人\N{\rE}Like it or not, we are masters of our fate.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:15.47,2:36:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没有注定的结局\N{\rE}Nothing is written.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:19.59,2:36:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,1996年5月22日
Dialogue: 0,2:36:20.98,2:36:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的事业\N{\rE}And our cause,
Dialogue: 0,2:36:23.39,2:36:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,无论多么正义\N{\rE}however righteous,
Dialogue: 0,2:36:24.94,2:36:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我们付出的努力\N{\rE}pales in comparison
Dialogue: 0,2:36:27.27,2:36:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和取得的成就相比\N{\rE}to the impact
Dialogue: 0,2:36:29.19,2:36:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,都显得不值一提\N{\rE}of our effect.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:34.32,2:36:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,对于美好未来的期许\N{\rE}Any hope for a better future
Dialogue: 0,2:36:36.91,2:36:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,都源于想让未来变成现实的冲动\N{\rE}comes from willing that future into being.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:40.33,2:36:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的未来也投射着我们的内心 有多么美好\N{\rE}A future reflecting the measure of good within ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:46.17,2:36:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,火控中心\N{\rE}Fire control!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:47.67,2:36:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对于我们内心所有的美好\N{\rE}And all that is good inside us...
Dialogue: 0,2:36:49.92,2:36:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,解除警戒\N{\rE}Stand down.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:51.13,2:36:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,衡量的方式就在于\N{\rE}...is measured by the good
Dialogue: 0,2:36:53.51,2:36:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做出的善举\N{\rE}we do for others.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:58.72,2:37:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拥有着同样的命运\N{\rE}We all share the same fate,
Dialogue: 0,2:37:01.31,2:37:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,同样的未来\N{\rE}the same future.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:03.34,2:37:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,立正
Dialogue: 0,2:37:04.68,2:37:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,2:37:06.85,2:37:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们无限次选择的结果\N{\rE}The sum of our infinite choices.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:12.19,2:37:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的未来建立在善良 信任\N{\rE}One such future is built on kindness, trust
Dialogue: 0,2:37:15.86,2:37:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和相互理解之上\N{\rE}and mutual understanding...
Dialogue: 0,2:37:21.79,2:37:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦我们\N{\rE}should we choose
Dialogue: 0,2:37:23.33,2:37:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,选择接受\N{\rE}to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:28.67,2:37:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不问归途地勇往直前\N{\rE}Driving without question...
Dialogue: 0,2:37:32.50,2:37:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,朝着看不见的光前行\N{\rE}towards a light we cannot see.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:38.55,2:37:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是为我们所珍爱之人\N{\rE}Not just for those we hold close...
Dialogue: 0,2:37:45.14,2:37:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 妈妈\N{\rE}Hi, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:46.60,2:37:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,也为不曾谋面之人\N{\rE}...but for those we'll never meet.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:53.36,2:37:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你明白 我永远爱你 兄弟\N{\rE}I hope you know I'll always love you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:57.91,2:38:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还会再见面的\N{\rE}And I will see you again.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:01.20,2:38:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不希望这一天太早到来\N{\rE}Though I hope it's not too soon.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:09.79,2:38:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界仍然需要你\N{\rE}The world still needs you.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:13.42,2:38:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 他们自己并不知道\N{\rE}Of course, they'll never know it.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:15.76,2:38:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们清楚\N{\rE}But we do.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:20.09,2:38:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我无论生死\N{\rE}We who live and die
Dialogue: 0,2:38:23.10,2:38:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,皆隐于世\N{\rE}in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:26.52,2:38:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这条信息五秒钟之后会自动销毁\N{\rE}This message will self-destruct in five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:32.61,2:38:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运 伊森\N{\rE}Good luck, Ethan.
